ed%20with%20the%20toaster%20oven.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22baked%20potato%20on%20a%20wire%20rack%20in%20a%20toaster%20oven%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657745800ec98e92f74e28fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20the%20toaster%20oven%20was%20preheated%2C%20I%20put%20the%20potato%20in%20for%20its%20first%20bake.%20%3Cp%3EPriscilla%20Thomas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20placed%20one%20of%20the%20prepped%20potatoes%20on%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-toaster-oven%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etoaster-oven%20rack%3C%2Fa%3E%20(with%20a%20clean%20drip%20pan%20underneath%20to%20catch%20any%20spills)%20and%20set%20a%2045-minute%20timer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20then%2C%20the%20potato%20was%20golden%20but%20not%20quite%20fully%20baked.%20I%20flipped%20it%20and%20placed%20it%20back%20in%20for%2015%20more%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20air-fryer%20potato%20went%20in%20for%2030%20minutes%20at%20400%20F.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224031%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22baked%20potato%20in%20an%20air%20fryer%20basket%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6577453658e7c0c29a2bacb4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223023%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20instructions%20for%20the%20air-fried%20baked%20potato%20called%20for%20a%20shorter%20cooking%20time.%20%3Cp%3EPriscilla%20Thomas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20placed%20the%20second%20potato%20directly%20in%20the%20air-fryer%20basket%20at%20400%20F.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20wasn't%20enough%20oil%20to%20drip%20and%20stick%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20my%20air%20fryer%2C%20so%20I%20was%20free%20to%20enjoy%20the%20heavenly%20aroma%20without%20dreading%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fcleaning-myths-making-your-home-dirtier%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20greasy%20cleanup%3C%2Fa%3E%20later%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20looked%20close%20to%20done%20after%2030%20minutes.%20But%20when%20I%20pierced%20it%20with%20a%20fork%2C%20it%20was%20still%20too%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20flip%20the%20potato%20and%20put%20it%20back%20in%20for%2015%20minutes%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhen%20both%20potatoes%20were%20finished%2C%20I%20cut%20them%20to%20check%20out%20their%20textures.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224031%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22baked%20potato%20cooked%20in%20an%20air%20fryer%20next%20to%20a%20baked%20potato%20cooked%20in%20a%20toaster%20oven%20on%20a%20white%20kitchen%20plate%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657746950ec98e92f74e29db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223023%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20air-fried%20potato%20(left)%20and%20my%20toaster-oven%20potato%20(right)%20after%20baking.%3Cp%3EPriscilla%20Thomas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20air-fried%20spud%20looked%20like%20a%20classic%20baked%20potato.%20The%20skin%20was%20firm%20and%20seemed%20crispy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20toaster-oven%20potato%20was%20lighter%20in%20color%20and%20less%20sturdy%20feeling%2C%20even%20though%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ftrying-10-minute-1-hour-10-hour-baked-potatoes-photos-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espent%20more%20time%20cooking%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20the%20inside%20of%20the%20air-fried%20potato%20wasn't%20creamy%20or%20fluffy%20like%20the%20skin%20made%20it%20seem.%20Instead%2C%20it%20was%20a%20bit%20stringy%2C%20similar%20to%20an%20overcooked%20parsnip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20toaster-oven%20potato%20had%20a%20fluffier%20inside%20%E2%80%94%20although%20parts%20of%20it%20seemed%20dry%20as%20if%20it%20hadn't%20cooked%20evenly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20terms%20of%20taste%2C%20the%20toaster-oven%20potato%20won.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222152%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22two%20baked%20potatoes%20cut%20open%20and%20mashed%20up%20on%20a%20white%20kitchen%20plate%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6577472c58e7c0c29a2baeab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221614%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20definitely%20preferred%20the%20toaster-oven%20potato%20the%20first%20time%20around.%20%3Cp%3EPriscilla%20Thomas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20the%20air-fried%20potato%20had%20this%20in%20the%20bag.%20But%20the%20flavor%20simply%20wasn't%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20inside%20tasted%20oddly%20sweet%2C%20again%20reminding%20me%20of%20parsnips.%20And%20the%20thick%20outer%20layer%20that%20seemed%20so%20promising%20turned%20out%20to%20lack%20flavor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20toaster-oven%20potato%20had%20more%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fbaked-potatoes-best-cooking-tips-from-chefs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclassic%20taste%20and%20interior%20texture%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20if%20I%20wanted%20it%20to%20have%20crispier%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20decided%20I%20needed%20to%20do%20a%20rematch%2C%20with%20some%20adjustments.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20baked%20potato%20in%20an%20air%20fryer%20basket%20and%20a%20baked%20potato%20on%20a%20rack%20in%20a%20toaster%20oven%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657747b57a3c8094d5dbac1d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20did%20the%20whole%20taste%20test%20again%20to%20account%20for%20any%20user%20error.%20%3Cp%3EPriscilla%20Thomas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20time%20around%2C%20I%20used%20a%20little%20more%20olive%20oil%20(about%202%20%C2%BD%20teaspoons%20per%20potato)%20and%20more%20seasoning%20(onion%20salt%2C%20garlic%20powder%2C%20and%20black%20pepper).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20gave%20both%20potatoes%20a%20little%20l