nded%2C%20nearly%20100%20parliamentarians%20have%20been%20suspended%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20amounts%20to%20nearly%20a%20quarter%20of%20all%20opposition%20MPs%20in%20the%20final%20full%20sitting%20of%20Parliament%20before%20next%20year's%20general%20election.%20The%20list%20of%20those%20suspended%20includes%20the%20Congress'%20Jairam%20Ramesh%2C%20KC%20Venugopal%2C%20and%20Randeep%20Surjewala%20from%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20From%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20Congress'%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20who%20is%20also%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%2C%20and%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%20have%20been%20suspended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Mr%20Gogoi%20criticised%20the%20government%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bsheer%20arrogance%26quot%3B%20of%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20for%20refusing%20to%20address%20Parliament%20after%20the%20security%20breach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20played%20out%20(in%20Parliament%20today)%20was%20the%20sheer%20arrogance%20of%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20who%20believes%20it%20is%20more%20appropriate%20to%20speak%20to%20a%20private%20TV%20channel%20than%20inside%20Parliament...%20to%20explain%20how%20there%20was%20a%20breach%20of%20security.%20How%20did%20four%20people%20conspire%20to%20enter%20Parliament%20without%20this%20powerful%20Home%20Minister%20knowing%20anything%3F%20This%20is%20an%20insecure%20Home%20Minister%2C%20who%20refuses%20to%20admit%20failure...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress'%20KV%20Venugopal%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20House%20is%20functioning%20with%20only%20one%20purpose...%20to%20suppress%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20opposition%20and%20to%20suspend%20maximum%20people...%20those%20who%20are%20raising%20issues%20of%20the%20people%20and%20national%20security.%20Now%2C%20Parliament%20is%20for%20suspension%2C%20not%20discussion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20saw%20nearly%20a%20dozen%20of%20her%20MPs%20suspended%2C%20including%20veteran%20Sougata%20Roy%2C%20Kakoli%20Ghosh%20Dastidar%2C%20and%20Kalyan%20Banerjee%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20said%20the%20government%20had%20%26quot%3Bno%20moral%20right%20to%20run%20a%20House%20(after)%20suspending%20the%20opposition%20fully%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20think%20the%20House%20is%20'supreme'%20why%20are%20they%20afraid%3F%20If%20they%20suspend%20all%20the%20members%2C%20who%20will%20raise%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20people%3F%20Voices%20of%20the%20people%20have%20been%20choked.%20They%20are%20passing%20three%20important%20bills...%20they%20have%20no%20moral%20right%20to%20suspend%20the%20opposition%20fully...%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702901820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fum6j1rso_new-parliament-building_625x300_19_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-100-mps-suspended-gaurav-gogoi-to-ndtv-arrogance-congress-mp-slams-amit-shah-after-nearly-100-mps-suspended-4697176%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Seventy-nine%20MPs%2C%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20were%20suspended%20Monday%20in%20an%20unprecedented%20development%20amid%20continuing%20fierce%20protests%20over%20last%20week's%20security%20breach.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-100-mps-suspended-gaurav-gogoi-to-ndtv-arrogance-congress-mp-slams-amit-shah-after-nearly-100-mps-suspended-4697176%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-100-mps-suspended-gaurav-gogoi-to-ndtv-arrogance-congress-mp-slams-amit-shah-after-nearly-100-mps-suspended-4697176%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-100-mps-suspended-gaurav-gogoi-to-ndtv-arrogance-congress-mp-slams-amit-shah-after-nearly-100-mps-suspended-46