3Bempowering%20the%20party%20to%20create%20an%20India%20rich%20in%20equal%20resource%20distribution%20and%20opportunities%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20cited%20the%20example%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20who%20also%20%26quot%3Btook%20donations%20from%20the%20public%20during%20the%20freedom%20struggle%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20payment%20link%20on%20the%20website%20prompts%20donors%20to%20make%20contributions%20of%20Rs%20138%20or%20Rs%201%2C380%20or%20Rs%2013%2C800%20to%20mark%20138%20years%20of%20the%20Congress%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20the%20Congress%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBeyond%20a%20campaign%2C%20it's%20a%20commitment%20to%20champion%20the%20rights%20of%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20bridge%20disparities%2C%20and%20stand%20as%20a%20formidable%20opposition%20against%20a%20government%20favouring%20the%20affluent%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20General%20Secretary%20(Organisation)%20KC%20Venugopal%20told%20the%20media%20yesterday%20that%20the%20campaign%20will%20primarily%20be%20online%20until%20December%2028%20-%20the%20party's%20foundation%20day%20-%20after%20which%20it%20will%20start%20a%20ground%20campaign%2C%20including%20door-to-door%20visits%20by%20volunteers%2C%20targeting%20at%20least%2010%20houses%20in%20every%20booth%20for%20contributions%20of%20at%20least%20Rs%20138%20from%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Venugopal%20said%20state-level%20office%20bearers%2C%20elected%20representatives%2C%20District%20Congress%20Committee%20presidents%2C%20PCC%20chiefs%20and%20AICC%20officials%20will%20be%20encouraged%20to%20contribute%20at%20least%20Rs%201%2C380%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20campaign's%20effectiveness%2C%20all%20PCC%20presidents%20will%20identify%20potential%20donors%20among%20the%20party's%20well-wishers%20and%20functionaries%2C%20aiming%20for%20contributions%20of%20Rs%201%2C380%20or%20Rs%2013%2C800.%20This%20strategic%20approach%20will%20ensure%20the%20success%20of%20o