%3EMarnie%20Griffiths%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%206-year-old%20asked%20for%20a%20cellphone%20for%20Christmas%2C%20and%20we%20are%20getting%20him%20one.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20says%20he%20wants%20it%20to%20be%20able%20to%20take%20photos%20of%20the%20insects%20and%20things%20he%20finds%20outside.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20are%20treating%20it%20just%20like%20another%20toy%2C%20and%20our%20only%20concern%20is%20that%20he'll%20break%20it%20or%20lose%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%202023%20survey%20by%20Common%20Sense%20Media%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.commonsensemedia.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fresearch%2Freport%2F2023-cs-smartphone-research-report_final-for-web.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E43%25%20of%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20own%20a%20smartphone%20by%20age%2012.%20At%206%20years%20old%2C%20our%20son%20will%20be%20ahead%20of%20the%20curve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20asked%20for%20two%20things%20this%20Christmas%3A%20a%20gnome%20house%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-phones%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecellphone%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He'll%20get%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20his%20dad%20and%20I%20encourage%20our%20children%20to%20use%20media%20puts%20us%20in%20the%20minority.%20A%20Pew%20Research%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Finternet%2F2020%2F07%2F28%2Fparenting-approaches-and-concerns-related-to-digital-devices%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estudy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20roughly%20seven%20in%2010%20parents%20think%20smartphones%20could%20bring%20more%20harm%20than%20good%20to%20children.%20Parents%20are%20afraid%20a%20cellphone%20will%20interfere%20with%20a%20child's%20ability%20to%20learn%20social%20skills%20and%20develop%20healthy%20friendships.%20Parents%20fear%20the%20devices%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-be-more-creative-constraint-generation-tips-neuroscience-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimpact%20their%20creativity%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20get%20in%20the%20way%20of%20developing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhobbies-successful-people-2017-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eother%20hobbies%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20see%20it%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20help%20his%20curiosity%20and%20nothing%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsneak-peek-at-toys-under-20-holiday-season-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanother%20toy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20saw%20the%20benefits%20of%20technology%20early%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20parents%2C%20we%20were%20initially%20ambivalent%20about%20giving%20our%20young%20toddler%20an%20iPad%20or%20setting%20the%20baby%20up%20in%20front%20of%20the%20TV.%20But%20even%20before%20the%20pandemic%20forced%20our%20hand%2C%20we%20came%20around%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20allowing%20our%20young%20children%20to%20explore%20technology%20and%20began%20recognizing%20the%20benefits%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20an%20early%20age%2C%20Oscar%20was%20a%20whiz%20on%20the%20iPad.%20He%20and%20his%20baby%20sister%20bonded%20over%20Blippi%20videos.%20He%20even%20taught%20himself%20how%20to%20skip%20ads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fprivate-kindergarten-costs-84000-were-making-school-district-pay-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egifted%20kid%3C%2Fa%3Es%2C%20Oscar%20gets%20really%20passionate%20about%20a%20particular%20subject%20matter.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20it's%20been%20fish%2C%20boats%2C%20the%20Titanic%2C%20mermaids%2C%20and%20gnomes.%20More%20recently%2C%20he's%20been%20getting%20into%20dragons.%20He%20loves%20nature%2C%20animals%2C%20and%20insects.%20YouTube%20is%20an%20accessible%20way%20to%20dive%20deeply%20and%20autonomously%20into%20these%20special%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHe%20wants%20a%20phone%20to%20use%20the%20camera%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20us%20he%20wants%20a%20cellphone%20for%20the%20camera%20feature%20so%20he%20can%20take%20pictures%20of%20the%20insects%20and%20animals%20he%20comes%20across%20at%20home%20and%20at%20school%2C%20and%20so%20that%20he%20can%20store%20and%20organize%20the%20pictures%20he%20takes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20tried%20buying%20him%20a%20top-rated%20digital%20camera%20made%20especially%20for%20kids%2C%20but%20it%20felt%20too%20much%20like%20a%20toy%20to%20him.%20Even%20if%20we%20tried%20buying%20him%20a%20real%20digital%20camera%2C%20I%20think%20he%20knows%20this%20is%20not%20what%20most%20grown-ups%20use%20to%20take%20pictures.%20He%20already%20takes%20pictures%20with%20our%20phones.%20He'll%20probably%20use%20his%20own%20phone%20to%20watch%20videos%2C%20too%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20OK%20with%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20treat%20it%20like%20any%20other%20toy%20he%20would%20ask%20for%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20we%20see%20it%2C%20there's%20no%20huge%20difference%20between%20a%20phone%20and%20a%20tablet%20or%20a%20computer.%20Maybe%20because%20they've%20always%20been%20available%2C%20our%20kids%20treat%20screens%20like%20toys.%20Honestly%2C%20there%20are%20times%20I'd%20prefer%20they%20were%20on%20the%20iPad%20instead%20of%20destroying%20the%20dining%20room%20with%20art-making%20materials%20or%20setting%20up%20elaborate%20obstacle%20courses%20all%20over%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20had%20our%20reservations%2C%20so%20we%20did%20a%20little%20research%20to%20see%20what%20experts%20said.%20I%20found%20that%2C%20like%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20we%20think%20of%20as%20risky%20for%20kids%2C%20there%20wasn't%20any%20evidence%20that%20cellphones%20are%20in%20any%20way%20detrimental.%20A%20rigorous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmed.stanford.edu%2Fnews%2Fall-news%2F2022%2F11%2Fchildren-mobile-phone-age.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E2022%20study%20from%C2%A0Stanford%20Medicine%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example%2C%C2%A0found%20no%20connection%20between%20the%20age%20children%20acquired%20their%20first%20cellphone%20and%20their%20sleep%20patterns%2C%20depression%20symptoms%2C%20or%20grades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20point%2C%20our%20only%20real%20concern%20is%20that%20he'll%20lose%20it%20or%20break%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAge%20readiness%2C%20experts%20say%2C%20depends%20on%20a%20child's%20unique%20abilities%20and%20personality.%20Our%20quirky%20and%20creative%206-year-old%20is%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgiving-kid-cell-phone-christmas-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702901281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656f884d7a3c8094d5d9dd6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgiving-kid-cell-phone-christmas-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22She's%20giving%20her%206-year-old%20a%20cell%20phone%20for%20Christmas%2C%20which%20he%20requested.%20He%20wants%20it%20for%20the%20camera%2C%20and%20the%20family%20plans%20to%20treat%20it%20like%20a%20toy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Melissa%20Petro)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgiving-kid-cell-phone-christmas-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BP%20joins%20firms%20in%20pausing%20all%20shipments%20through%20Red%20Sea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702901160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F70x70%2Fskynews-houthi-galaxy-leader_6396904.jpg%3F20231218124752%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbp-pauses-all-shipments-of-oil-through-red-sea-after-attacks-by-houthi-rebels-13033483%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20growing%20number%20of%20companies%