0Aadhaar-Like%20Identity%20Verification%20System%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21211445%2FAadhaar-1200x560-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Taking%20forward%20India%E2%80%99s%20offer%20for%20a%20grant%20to%20the%20former%20Rajapaksa%20regime%20to%20fund%20an%20Aadhaar-like%20identity%20verification%20system%20for%20its%20citizens%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20has%20entered%20into%20an%20agreement%20with%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20to%20start%20work%20%E2%80%9Con%20basic%20level%20issues%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20project%20from%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20December%2017%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sundayobserver.lk%2F2023%2F12%2F17%2Fnews%2F12553%2Fdigital-id-cards-from-next-month%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%3Cem%3ESunday%20Observer%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20agreement%20was%20reached%20%E2%80%9Cduring%20a%20discussion%20held%20last%20week%20between%20Indian%20Government%20representatives%20and%20the%20(Sri%20Lankan)%20President%E2%80%99s%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20and%20(its)%20National%20Security%20Adviser%20Sagala%20Ratnayaka.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20the%20new%20digital%20ID%20card%20to%20be%20funded%20by%20India%20would%20cost%20Rs%20400%20crore%2C%20and%20would%20include%20biometric%20data%2C%20such%20as%20the%20holder%E2%80%99s%20eye%20colour%2C%20fingerprints%2C%20and%20blood%20type.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%2076%20biometrics%20were%20needed%20for%20digital%20IDs%2C%20but%20the%20updated%20version%20will%20need%20only%20six.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20(Sri%20Lankan%20)%20Government%20aims%20to%20first%20issue%20the%20updated%20digital%20ID%20card%20for%20new%20applicants%20and%20then%20gradually%20introduce%20it%20to%20the%20entire%20population%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202022%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%2