ing%20this%20to%20the%20public.%20Also%20we%20have%20asked%20our%20hospitals%20and%20health%20centres%20to%20be%20prepared.%20There%20should%20be%20more%20surveillance%20in%20border%20districts%20like%20--%20Kodagu%2C%20Dakshina%20Kannada%2C%20Chamarajanagara%20--%20which%20share%20border%20with%20Kerala%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20would%2C%20based%20on%20the%20situation%2C%20decide%20what%20further%20measures%20need%20to%20be%20taken%2C%20he%20said.%20Along%20with%20stepping%20up%20surveillance%20at%20the%20border%2C%20instructions%20have%20been%20issued%20to%20increase%20testing%20and%20those%20with%20symptoms%20and%20suspicious%20cases%20are%20being%20asked%20to%20compulsorily%20undergo%20testing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20we%20will%20get%20to%20know%20if%20the%20infections%20are%20increasing%20or%20not.%20As%20we%20increase%20COVID%20tests%2C%20if%20more%20positive%20cases%20are%20recorded%2C%20we%20will%20decide%20on%20further%20measures%20that%20need%20to%20be%20taken.%20There%20is%20no%20need%20for%20imposing%20any%20curbs%20or%20restrictions%20now%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20whether%20there%20will%20be%20any%20restriction%20on%20Ayyappa%20pilgrims%20returning%20from%20Kerala%2C%20Rao%20said%2C%20as%20of%20now%20there%20are%20no%20curbs%20on%20restriction%20on%20movement%20of%20people%20and%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20not%20stop%20any%20such%20thing%20now%2C%20because%20such%20a%20situation%20--%20where%20people%20should%20not%20move%20or%20gather%20--%20is%20not%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20monitor%20the%20situation%20daily%2C%20in%20case%20we%20get%20any%20adverse%20information%2C%20we%20will%20say%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20done.%20For%20those%20above%2060%20years%20of%20age%2C%20those%20with%20comorbidities%20and%20respiratory%20issues%2C%20wearing%20masks%20is%20good.%20We%20will%20make%20it%20mandatory.%20Advisory%20will%20be%20issued%20by%20the%20government%20today.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20a%20mock%20drill%20has%20been%20conducted%20at%20all%20hospitals%20by%20district%20health%20officials%20to%20check%20their%20preparedness%2C%20the%20Minister%20said%2C%20checks%20have%20been%20conducted%20on%20the%20number%20of%20beds%2C%20ventilators%2C%20oxygen%20supply%2C%20masks%2C%20testing%20and%20PPE%20kits%20among%20other%20things%20that%20are%20required%20in%20case%20of%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstructions%20have%20been%20given%20to%20make%20necessary%20preparations%20at%20all%20health%20centres%20and%20taluk%20and%20district%20hospitals%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rao%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702898940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2Flok6m018_covid-india-coronavirus_625x300_22_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fkarnataka-mask-advisory-for-senior-citizens-as-covid-cases-rise-in-kerala-4696127%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Karnataka%20government%20on%20Monday%20asked%20those%20above%2060-years%20of%20age%2C%20with%20comorbidities%2C%20and%20symptoms%20of%20cough%2C%20phlegm%20and%20fever%20to%20mandatorily%20wear%20face%20masks%2C%20in%20the%20wake%20detection%20of%20a%20case%20of%20COVID-19%20sub-variant%20JN.1%20in%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fkarnataka-mask-advisory-for-senior-citizens-as-covid-cases-rise-in-kerala-4696127%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fkarnataka-mask-advisory-for-senior-citizens-as-covid-cases-rise-in-kerala-4696127%2Fam