20even%20more%20protection.%20If%20you%20couldn't%20tell%20yet%2C%20I'm%20a%20freak%20about%20avoiding%20the%20sun.%20I'm%20trying%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fdr-pimple-poppers-nighttime-skincare-routine-3-steps-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreserve%20my%20smooth%20skin%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20youthful%20glow%20for%20as%20long%20as%20possible%2C%20since%20it's%20part%20of%20my%20appeal%20to%20clients.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMy%20dermatologist%20said%20that%20my%20face%20could%20still%20get%20exposed%20to%20UV%20rays%20even%20when%20I%20wear%20a%20wide-brim%20hat%2C%20so%20I%20came%20up%20with%20this%20solution.%20I%20even%20wear%20it%20in%20cars%2C%20since%20windows%20can't%20completely%20block%20the%20sun's%20effects.%20I%20may%20look%20strange%20in%20public%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20care%20because%20I%20know%20it's%20a%20good%20business%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decide%20to%20check%20out%20a%20tech-forward%20wellness%20spa%2C%20since%20I%20have%20a%20gift%20card%20there%20from%20an%20escort%20client.%20He's%20equally%20as%20stressed%20out%20as%20I%20am%20about%20work%2C%20so%20I%20know%20I%20can%20trust%20his%20recommendation.%20I%20kiss%20my%20cat%20Lucy%20goodbye%20and%20hop%20in%20an%20Uber%20to%20the%20spa%2C%20where%20I%20try%20out%20their%20infrared%20sauna%20and%20hyperbaric%20chamber.%20I%20put%20my%20face%20mask%20back%20on%2C%20and%20walk%20out%20feeling%20like%20a%20new%20person.%20%26quot%3BYou%20should%20do%20this%20more%20often%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20tell%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lucy%2C%20Lee's%20cat%2C%20counts%20some%20of%20her%20earnings.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b62c30ec98e92f74fa5de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELucy%2C%20Lee's%20cat%2C%20counts%20some%20of%20her%20earnings.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Mia%20Lee%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20g