hich%20is%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20text%20my%20assistant.%20I%20like%20to%20be%20honest%20with%20my%20clients%2C%20because%20if%20they%20want%20my%20time%20and%20attention%2C%20they'll%20make%20it%20work.%20They%20can%20either%20choose%20another%20time%2C%20or%20book%20a%20longer%20date.%20He%20tells%20my%20assistant%20he'll%20take%20a%20two-hour%20slot%20for%20lunch%20next%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20year%2C%20I%20usually%20prioritize%20bookings%20from%20my%20escort%20clients%2C%20not%20stripping%20at%20the%20club.%20With%20stripping%2C%20there's%20no%20guarantee%20I'll%20make%20a%20set%20amount%20of%20money.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20factors%20at%20play%20%E2%80%94%20how%20many%20clients%20book%20private%20rooms%2C%20how%20much%20they%20tip%2C%20and%20if%20they%20pay%20with%20cash%20or%20a%20credit%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20club%20is%20bustling%20right%20now.%20Many%20of%20my%20out-of-town%20strip-club%20regulars%20have%20returned%20to%20the%20city%20for%20pre-Christmas%20business%20meetings%20and%20company%20holiday%20parties.%20The%20club's%20private%20rooms%20are%20in%20high%20demand%20right%20now%2C%20so%20I%20can%20count%20on%20them%20to%20pay%20for%20at%20least%20four%20hours%20alone%20with%20me%2C%20which%20will%20set%20them%20back%20a%20minimum%20of%20%241%2C760.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20busy%20season%20we're%20in%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20negotiate%20with%20clients%2C%20so%20I'm%20planning%20on%20making%20even%20more.%20I%20can%20tell%20one%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20not%20going%20to%20pay%20me%20more%2C%20I'm%20walking%20out%20of%20this%20room%20and%20I'll%20get%20another%20room%20with%20a%20paying%20client.%26quot%3B%20Instant%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221673%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mia%20Lee%20is%20a%20professional%20escort%20in%20New%20York%20City.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b634950edbc52a86469a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221804%5C%2