20hired%20her%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20it's%20been%20life-changing.%20She%20comes%20over%20once%20a%20week%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20whether%20I'm%20home%20or%20not%2C%20to%20tidy%20my%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20takes%20care%20of%20my%20laundry%20and%20dry%20cleaning%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20it.%20I%20put%20the%20lingerie%20set%20I%20wore%20last%20night%2C%20and%20the%20three%20nights%20prior%2C%20in%20a%20dry-cleaning%20bag%20so%20she%20can%20take%20it%20on%20her%20way%20out.%20I'll%20wear%20the%20same%20set%20a%20bunch%20before%20laundering%20it%2C%20since%20I%20don't%20sweat.%20Thank%20you%2C%20cosmetic%20surgery.%20I%20have%20four%20lingerie%20sets%20and%20cycle%20through%20them%20each%20week.%20Other%20dancers%20have%20full%20wardrobes%20of%20club%20attire%2C%20but%20I%20prefer%20my%20method%2C%20since%20it%20saves%20money%2C%20and%20time%20that%20I'd%20rather%20spend%20with%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20my%20housekeeper%20cleans%20and%20organizes%2C%20I%20get%20back%20in%20bed%20for%20another%20nap%20and%20set%20my%20alarm%20for%208%20p.m.%20%E2%80%94I%20like%20to%20give%20myself%20at%20least%20an%20hour%20to%20wake%20up%20and%20mentally%20prepare%20for%20my%20shifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20arrive%20at%20the%20club%20at%209%20p.m.%20Five%20minutes%20later%2C%20I'm%20in%20a%20private%20room%20with%20one%20of%20my%20regulars.%20I%20get%20another%20girl%20to%20join%20us%2C%20and%20we%20spend%20six%20hours%20entertaining%20him%20with%20a%20few%20breaks%20in%20between.%20He%20tips%20us%20%242%2C300%20in%20cash%2C%20and%20we%20split%20the%20spoils.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20get%20home%20at%203%3A30%20a.m.%20and%20go%20straight%20to%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThursday%2C%20December%2014%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wake%20up%20at%20noon%2C%20brush%20my%20teeth%2C%20and%20do%20some%20more%20administrative%20work%20before%20I%20head%20to%20a%20client%20who%20is%20waiting%20for%20me%20at%20midtown%20Manhattan%20hotel%20for%20a%20two-hour%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221371%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mia%20Lee%20stands%20in%20Central%20Park.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b64130ec98e92f74fa66c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221028%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELee%20often%20meets%20her%20escort%20clients%20at%20luxury%20hotels%20in%20Midtown%20Manhattan%2C%20or%20accompanies%20them%20to%20networking%20dinners%2C%20posing%20as%20their%20sexy%20and%20smart%20girlfriend.%3Cp%3EPenelope%20Dario%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20take%20home%20the%20car%20he's%20called%20for%20me.%20As%20I%20get%20home%2C%20I%20see%20he's%20sent%20a%20%241%2C000%20tip.%20The%20extra%20cash%20makes%20dozing%20off%20in%20bed%20with%20Lucy%20feel%20extra%20satisfying.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWhen%20I%20wake%20up%2C%20I%20put%20on%20a%20white%20lingerie%20set%20and%20then%20walk%20to%20the%20club.%20After%20a%20few%20hours%20with%20a%20private%20client%2C%20another%20dancer%20asks%20if%20I'll%20go%20with%20her%20to%20bring%20a%20group%20of%20regulars%20currently%20partying%20at%20the%20bar%20down%20the%20street%20back%20to%20the%20club.%20She%20promises%20it%20will%20take%2015%20minutes%2C%20so%20I%20agree%20to%20help%20her%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20head%20over%20around%2010%20p.m.%20and%20order%20a%20glass%20of%20red%20wine%20that%20I%20sip%20on%20for%20five%20minutes.%20It's%20nearing%20the%2015-minute%20mark%20when%20they%20close%20the%20bill%20and%20we%20walk%20back%20to%20the%20club.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20immediately%20click%20with%20one%20of%20the%20guys%2C%20so%20we%20head%20straight%20to%20a%20private%20room%20when%20we%20get%20to%20the%20club.%20I%20spend%20a%20half-hour%20with%20him%2C%20and%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-much-strippers-make-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egives%20me%20a%20%241%2C000%20tip%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20I%20dance%20in%20t