0four%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702897200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fak8sdai_track-flooded-1200_625x300_18_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F500-passengers-stuck-as-tamil-nadu-station-flooded-amid-heavy-rain-tracks-damaged-4696450%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Around%20500%20passengers%20on%20Monday%20were%20stuck%20at%20a%20Tamil%20Nadu%20railway%20station%20after%20heavy%20rain%20battered%20the%20southern%20parts%20of%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F500-passengers-stuck-as-tamil-nadu-station-flooded-amid-heavy-rain-tracks-damaged-4696450%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F500-passengers-stuck-as-tamil-nadu-station-flooded-amid-heavy-rain-tracks-damaged-4696450%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F500-passengers-stuck-as-tamil-nadu-station-flooded-amid-heavy-rain-tracks-damaged-4696450%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trafficked%2C%20Sold%2C%20Abused%20Then%20Rescued%20From%20Iraq%3A%20Punjabi%20Women%20Share%20Their%20Ordeal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18162840%2Fclaudia-soraya-3m15w5sirVs-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJalandhar%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EManpreet%20Kaur%20was%20one%20of%20the%20many%20young%20women%20who%20was%20trafficked%20to%20Iraq%20by%20a%20nexus%20of%20fake%20travel%20agents%20with%20roots%20in%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20Kapurthala%20and%20Jalandhar%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManpreet%2C%20like%20many%20other%20women%2C%20had%20refused%20to%20work%20as%20a%20domestic%20worker%20without%20a%20salary%20and%20resisted%20the%20advances%20of%20the%20house%20owner%20and%20agents%20who%20used%20to%20come%20to%20%E2%80%98buy%E2%80%99%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20Manpreet%20along%20with%2015%20others%20managed%20to%20return%20home%20from%20Iraq%2C%20following%20the%20timely%20efforts%20of%20AAP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Baba%20Balbir%20Singh%20Seechewal%20and%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs.%20Manpreet%20and%20her%20friend%20Sandeep%20came%20back%20on%20November%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20was%20beaten%2C%20kicked%20in%20the%20stomach%2C%20and%20locked%20inside%20a%20washroom%2C%20a%20Nepali%20woman%2C%20who%20too%20was%20kept%20as%20a%20domestic%20worker%2C%20was%20dragged%20from%20the%20stairs%2C%20stripped%20naked%20and%20made%20to%20stand%20on%20the%20highway%20by%20the%20landlord.%20She%20was%20presented%20before%20the%20%E2%80%98agents%2C%E2%80%99%20who%20had%20come%20to%20buy%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20hushed%20voice%2C%20Manpreet%2C%20who%20sustained%20internal%20injuries%20and%20was%20undergoing%20treatment%20at%20a%20relative%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20said%20that%20nobody%20came%20forward%20to%20save%20that%20Nepali%20woman%20%E2%80%93%20neither%20the%20women%20in%20the%20house%20nor%20any%20passers-by.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20terrified%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20even%20a%20slight%20glance%20from%20the%20men%20towards%20us%20would%20send%20shivers%20down%20our%20spine.%20Even%20now%2C%20when%20I%20recall%20those%20moments%2C%20I%20feel%20faint%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20ordeal%20was%20not%20just%20confined%20to%20physical%20abuse%3B%20the%20Iraqi%20nationals%20allegedly%20used%20to%20harass%20them%20by%20not%20giving%20them%20anything%20to%20eat.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20days%20I%20would%20remain%20hungry.%20To%20top%20it%20all%2C%20they%20used%20to%20ask%20us%20to%20cut%20meat%20pieces%2C%20which%20was%20an%20extremely%20abhorrent%20task%20to%20do.%20They%20used%20to%20punish%20the%20women%20in%20weird%20ways%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20while%20continuously%20thanking%20god%20for%20saving%20her%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20around%2060%20women%20have%20been%20rescued%20by%20Baba%20Seechewal%20from%20the%20Gulf%20countries%20of%20Oman%2C%20Iraq%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20bringing%20to%20the%20fore%20the%20thriving%20nexus%20of%20human%20traffickers%20and%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20police%20to%20set%20things%20right.%20Earlier%2C%20another%20AAP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20Vikamjit%20Singh%20Sahney%2C%20had%20also%20rescued%20many%20Punjabi%20women%20stuck%20in%20the%20Gulf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsually%2C%20the%20women%20are%20promised%20jobs%20as%20domestic%20workers%20in%20hotels%2C%20malls%20and%20hospitals%20in%20the%20Gulf%20nations.%20However%2C%20the%20reality%20is%20that%20the%20moment%20they%20land%20in%20the%20Gulf%2C%20they%20are%20sold%20to%20some%20other%20agents%2C%20who%20either%20keep%20them%20as%20slaves%20or%20force%20them%20to%20join%20prostitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20computer%20graduate%20but%20the%20travel%20agents%20trapped%20me%20too.%20The%20desire%20to%20overcome%20poverty%20and%20lead%20a%20better%20life%20pushed%20me%20towards%20this%20nexus%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manpreet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWomen%20share%20their%20ordeal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20avoid%20any%20immigration%20staff%20queries%2C%20the%20woman%20were%20first%20taken%20to%20Dubai.%20After%20making%20them%20wait%20for%20around%20eight%20hours%20at%20the%20Dubai%20airport%2C%20they%20were%20issued%20Iraq%20visas.%20The%20moment%20they%20landed%20in%20Iraq%2C%20their%20passports%20and%20mobile%20phones%20were%20allegedly%20snatched%20by%20the%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20travel%20agents%20also%20gave%20them%20job%20letters%20from%20a%20cleaning%20company%20in%20Sulaymaniyah%2C%20Iraq%2C%20so%20that%20the%20women%20were%20convinced%20that%20they%20had%20a%20valid%20work%20visa.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20employed%20in%20one%20%E2%80%98Machak%20Company%E2%80%99%2C%20Sulaymaniyah%20where%20women%20from%20different%20countries%20like%20India%2C%20Nepal%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20African%20countries%20were%20hired%20for%20menial%20jobs%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20victim%2C%20Sandeep%20Kaur%20from%20Kapurthala%20district%2C%20said%20they%20realised%20why%20the%20travel%20agents%20did%20not%20send%20them%20directly%20to%20Iraq%20from%20India.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20an%20hour-long%20flight%20from%20Dubai%20to%20Iraq%2C%20from%20where%20we%20were%20first%20taken%20to%20the%20Machak%20Company%20office%2C%20which%20gave%20us%20job%20letters.%20From%20there%20some%20men%20came%20to%20pick%20us%20up%20in%20cars%20and%20we%20were%20sent%20to%20different%20locations.%20Our%20nightmare%20started%20the%20moment%20we%20were%20employed%20as%20domestic%20workers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sandeep%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20the%20women%20travel%20agent%20through%20whom%20Sandeep%20reached%20Iraq%20was%20her%20relative.%20%E2%80%9CMandeep%20Kaur%20from%20Phagwara%2C%20Kapurthala%20district%20is%20a%20distant%20relative.%20She%20has%20been%20living%20in%20Iraq%20for%20two%20years.%20She%20used%20to%20call%20us%20from%20Iraq%20and%20share%20stories%20about%20her%20comfortable%20life.%20But%20once%20we%20landed%20in%20Iraq%2C%20she%20stopped%20responding%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sandeep%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20woman%2C%20requesting%20anonymity%2C%20said%20they%20wanted%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20Mandeep%20for%20help%20but%20she%20just%20left%20them%20alone.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20many%20woman%20who%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20timely%20assistance%20and%20lack%20of%20funds%20were%20trapped%20in%20the%20vicious%20circle%20of%20slavery%20and%20prostitution.%20We%20met%20some%20Nepali%20women%20who%20had%20been%20staying%20in%20Iraq%20for%20the%20last%20seven-eight%20years%20and%20their%20condition%20was%20miserable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFearing%20social%20stigma%2C%20the%20women%20decided%20not%20to%20lodge%20FIRs%20personally.%20Their%20cases%20were%20taken%20up%20by%20Baba%20Seechewal%20with%20senior%20police%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWomen%20travel%20agents%E2%80%99%20network%20on%20the%20rise%20in%20villages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trend%20of%20women%20acting%20as%20touts%20or%20brokers%20is%20on%20the%20rise%20in%20Punjab%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20NRI%20rich%20belt%20of%20Jalandhar%2C%20Hoshiarpur%2C%20Kapurthala%20and%20Nawanshahr%20districts.%20The%20agents%20are%20trapping%20women%20from%20financially%20weaker%20sections%20aged%20around%2018%20to%2035%20years%20in%20the%20villages%20and%20are%20allegedly%20responsible%20for%20pushing%20them%20into%20prostitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMandeep%20Kaur%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Phagwara%20town%20in%20Kapurthala%20district%20who%20is%20currently%20living%20in%20Iraq%2C%20was%20named%20by%20both%20Manpreet%20and%20Sandeep%20as%20the%20person%20who%20they%20were%20in%20contact%20with%20about%20moving%20to%20Iraq.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20also%20shared%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20gang%20of%20around%2020%20to%2025%20people%20led%20by%20Indians%2C%20Pakistanis%20and%20Iraqis%20in%20which%20Mandeep%20was%20from%20Phagwara%2C%20and%20three%20men%20were%20from%20Nawanshahr%20district%2C%20Kartarpur%20town%20in%20Jalandhar%20and%20Zira%20town%20in%20Ferozepur%20district%20respectively.%20While%20Mandeep%20lures%20woman%20with%20work%20visas%20in%20Iraq%2C%20her%20male%20counterparts%20decide%20where%20the%20women%20will%20actually%20go.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20said%20that%20initially%2C%20Mandeep%20lured%20them%20with%20a%20free%20work%20visa%20offer%20in%20Iraq%20but%20when%20finally%20their%20visa%20came%2C%20she%20demanded%20Rs%2080%2C000.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20paid%20Rs%2080%2C000%20each%20plus%20another%20Rs%2025%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManpreet%20said%20that%20she%20carried%20an%20extra%20amount%20of%20Rs%206%2C000%20for%20her%20personal%20expenses%20but%20Mandeep%20snatched%20that%20too.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20biggest%20shock%20came%20when%20the%20men%20in%20the%20house%20told%20us%20that%20they%20had%20bought%20us%20and%20we%20should%20pay%20them%20Rs%204%20lakh%2C%20if%20we%20wanted%20to%20go%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAAP%20MP%20raises%20issue%20in%20parliament%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%206%2C%20Baba%20Seechewal%20raised%20this%20issue%20in%20parliament%20and%20demanded%20strict%20vigilance%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20to%20track%20the%20nexus%20of%20fake%20travel%20agents%20and%20their%20touts%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20whom%20manage%20to%20flee%20because%20of%20tardy%20police%20investigations%20and%20out%20of%20court%20settlements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20speech%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWomen%20and%20girls%20are%20being%20taken%20to%20Gulf%20countries%20through%20travel%20agents%20and%20sold%20there.%20Through%20our%20efforts%20and%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%2C%20we%20have%20brought%20back%20to%20India%20around%2060%20women%20from%20Gulf%20countries%20who%20were%20trafficked%20there.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTravel%20agents%20are%20trapping%20very%20young%20women%2Fgirls%20from%20poor%20households%20and%20sending%20them%20on%20visitor%20visas%20to%20Gulf%20countries%20where%20they%20are%20being%20exploited.%20They%20are%20tricked%20into%20working%20in%20homes%20or%20in%20restaurants%20and%20falsely%20assured%20of%20salaries%20of%20Rs%2035%2C000%20to%2040%2C000.%20Then%2C%20those%20women%20are%20made%20to%20sign%20an%20agreement%20written%20in%20Arabic%20language%2C%20which%20is%20being%20taken%20undue%20advantage%20of.%20It%20is%20a%20large%20group%20of%20people%20whose%20network%20is%20spread%20across%20different%20states%20of%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDGP%20Punjab%20orders%20probe%2C%20no%20headway%20yet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20note%20of%20these%20cases%2C%20Baba%20Seechewal%20met%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20(DGP)%20Punjab%20Gaurav%20Yadav%20in%20October%20and%20sought%20strict%20action%20against%20the%20culprits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Seechewal%20said%20that%20the%20DGP%20had%20assured%20him%20that%20he%20would%20appoint%20a%20committee%20headed%20by%20Deputy%20Inspector%20General%20(DIG)%20Jalandhar%20Range%20as%20nodal%20officer%20and%20Senior%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(SSP)%20Jalandhar%20and%20Kapurthala%20as%20members%20to%20investigate%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20months%20after%20the%20constitution%20of%20the%20DIG-level%20committee%2C%20though%2C%20there%20does%20not%20appear%20to%20have%20been%20much%20movement.%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0reached%20out%20to%20DIG%20Jalandhar%20Range%20S.%20Bhoopathi%20with%20a%20questionnaire%20but%20failed%20to%20get%20an%20response.%20The%20DIG%20had%20initially%20responded%20to%20text%20messages%20but%20later%20stopped%20doing%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20contacted%20SSP%20Kapurthala%20Vatsala%20Gupta%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20investigation%20is%20at%20a%20preliminary%20stage%20and%20as%20it%20is%20a%20sensitive%20case%2C%20we%20cannot%20reveal%20much.%20But%20there%20is%20no%20denying%20that%20the%20trend%20of%20women%20acting%20as%20travel%20agents%20or%20brokers%20as%20part%20of%20a%20big%20human%20trafficking%20racket%20is%20on%20the%20rise%20in%20Punjab.%20A%20major%20fault%20also%20lies%20on%20the%20part%20of%20people%20who%20apply%20for%20such%20visas%2C%20as%20despite%20widespread%20awareness%20campaigns%2C%20people%20do%20not%20tend%20to%20verify%20the%20details%20of%20the%20travel%20agents%20and%20then%20get%20stuck.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20said%20that%20he%20also%20handed%20over%20a%20list%20of%20some%20travel%20agents%20to%20expedite%20the%20investigation.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20waiting%20for%20a%20police%20probe%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENRI%20affairs%20minister%20clueless%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Punjab%20NRI%20affairs%20minister%20Kuldeep%20Singh%20Dhaliwal%20also%20failed%20to%20give%20an%20elaborate%20reply%20to%20most%20of%20the%20queries%20posed%20by%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20minister%20said%20that%20he%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20magnitude%20of%20the%20problem%20and%20was%20working%20to%20break%20the%20nexus%20of%20fraud%20travel%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20expressing%20deep%20concern%20over%20the%20flourishing%20fake%20travel%20agents%E2%80%99%20nexus%20in%20the%20NRI%20rich%20belt%20of%20Jalandhar%2C%20Kapurthala%2C%20Nawanshahr%20and%20Hoshiarpur%20districts%2C%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20aware%20how%20women%20travel%20agents%20walk%20around%20the%20villages%20and%20trap%20women%20from%20financially%20weak%20backgrounds%20with%20big%20dreams%20of%20work%20visa%2C%20job%20and%20good%20salary.%20We%20are%20tracking%20these%20cases%20and%20will%20make%20some%20headway%20soon.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhaliwal%20also%20said%20that%20he%20had%20brought%20this%20matter%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20laws%20to%20track%20and%20punish%20human%20trafficking%20were%20the%20central%20government%E2%80%99s%20domain%2C%20we%20have%20raised%20this%20issue%20with%20the%20MHA%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3ENames%20changed%20to%20protect%20victims%E2%80%99%20anonymity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702897169000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18162840%2Fclaudia-soraya-3m15w5sirVs-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftrafficked-sold-abused-then-rescued-from-iraq-punjabi-women-share-their-ordeal%22%2C%22s