esthetically%20appealing%20walled%20campuses%20curated%20by%20the%20corporate%20capital%20are%20tailor-made%20for%20the%20privileged.%20Parental%20aspirations%20are%20reproduced%20in%20a%20space%20that%20guarantees%20exclusivity%20and%20isolation.%20It%20is%20a%20fancy%20campus-life%20that%20can%20be%20accessed%20by%20a%20limited%20clientele.%20It%20is%20devoid%20of%20any%20pretension%20of%20social%20justice%20and%20egalitarian%20values%20of%20education-for-all.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fashoka-universitys-descent-into-academic-unfreedom%5C%22%3EAshoka%20University%E2%80%99s%20Descent%20into%20Academic%20(un)Freedom%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EClass%20and%20caste%20homogeneity%20of%20private%20universities%20defies%20heterogeneity%2C%20inclusivity%20and%20the%20ideal%20that%20a%20university%20is%20a%20levelling-field.%20With%20a%20non-existent%20representation%20of%20the%20unprivileged%2C%20and%20students%20from%20the%20state-boards%20%E2%80%93%20the%20message%20is%20loud%20and%20clear%3A%20rights%20to%20education%20are%20abjectly%20reserved%2C%20and%20unapologetically%20so.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20varied%20pedagogic%20choice-basket%20and%20curriculum-flexibility%2C%20these%20universities%20act%20as%20functional%20preparatory-schools%20for%20a%20foreign%20post-graduate%20endeavour.%20Barely%20any%20students%20coming%20out%20of%20these%20institutions%20yearn%20to%20enter%20public%20universities%20in%20India%20for%20research%20or%20further%20studies.%20While%20Rs%2050%20lakhs%20may%20appear%20shockingly%20absurd%20for%20many%20to%20buy%20a%20degree%20in%20social%20sciences%20and%20humanities%2C%20but%20a%20similar%20sort%20of%20an%20under-grad%20degree%20from%20the%20US%20or%20Europe%2C%20may%20cost%20twice%20as%20much.%20So%20those%20who%20are%20choosing%20to%20spend%20that%20much%20are%20possibly%20saving%20more%20by%20deferring%20and%20delaying%20their%20flights%20abroad.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConsciously%20quarantined%20from%20its%20immediate%20surroundings%2C%20these%20are%20utopian%20and%20apolitical%20spaces.%20Located%20on%20recently%20commercialised%20pastoral-lands%20located%20at%20the%20far-end%20of%20metropolitan-limits%2C%20these%20are%20islands%20that%20are%20heavily%20guarded%20from%20the%20controversies%20of%20caste%2C%20marginality%2C%20malnutrition%2C%20poverty%20and%20a%20host%20of%20other%20pertinent%20issues%20that%20exist%20outside%20its%20gate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18150418%2Fashoka-bckgd.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18150418%2Fashoka-bckgd.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18150418%2Fashoka-bckgd-300x182.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18150418%2Fashoka-bckgd-1024x622.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689659%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22729%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAshoka%20University%20Campus%2CRaya%2CSoniepat%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20in%20the%20name%20of%20safety%20and%20security%2C%20its%20high%20boundaries%20immunise%20students%20inside%20from%20the%20everyday-realities%20of%20the%20life%20outside%20the%20campus.%20Much%20hyped-up%20emphasis%20on%20%E2%80%98critical-thinking%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98interdisciplinarity%E2%80%99%20are%20successfully%20sold%20catch-words%20that%20tends%20to%20overlook%20socio-political%20concerns%20of%20its%20proximity.%20The%20question%20remains%20as%20to%20what%20extent%20can%20a%20true%20social%20science%20training%20be%20fostered%20within%20such%20social%20isolation.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20inherent%20mandate%20of%20social%20science%20education%20is%20to%20challenge%20the%20existing%20power-structures%20and%20status-quo.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20expression%20of%20dissent%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20social-science%20training.%20With%20assured%20protection%20of%20class-interest%2C%20one%20doubts%20how%20much%20%E2%80%98critical-thinking%E2%80%99%20in%20classrooms%20can%20possibly%20translate%20into%20critical-action%20outside%20the%20campus.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProtest%20and%20resistance%20are%20non-existent%20in%20private%20universities%2C%20not%20because%20of%20an%20institutional%20apathy%20for%20dissent%2C%20but%20because%20protests%20are%20made%20to%20appear%20irrelevant.%20These%20fully%20residential-campus-lives%20operate%20like%20regiments%20with%20a%20host%20of%20curfews%2C%20restrictions%20and%20repression-mechanisms.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fashoka-university-strike-academic-freedom-sabyasachi-das%5C%22%3EThe%20Significance%20of%20Ashoka%20University%E2%80%99s%20Teachers%20Calling%20for%20a%20Strike%20Over%20Academic%20Freedom%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERepressive%20administrative%20bureaucracy%20is%20often%20staffed%20by%20ex-army-men%2C%20who%20may%20consider%20peaceful%20mobilisation%20as%20an%20act%20of%20indiscipline.%20Young%20adults%20are%20often%20infantilised.%20At%20times%2C%20worse%20than%20parental%20injunctions%2C%20these%20injunctions%20are%20normalised%2C%20as%20students%20get%20socialised%20to%20remain%20under%20severe%20surveillance.%20The%20prized%20freedom%20to%20choose%20and%20change%20courses%20often%20comes%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20personal%20freedom%20that%20once%20characterised%20our%20college%20lives.%20Surrounded%20by%20perceived%20dangers%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edehat%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(rural%20areas)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20these%20sanitised%20spaces%20have%20serious%20exit-issues%20%E2%80%93%20barring%20the%20promise%20of%20preparing%20students%20to%20go%20abroad.%20When%20%E2%80%98foreign%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20destination%2C%20why%20waste%20time%20engaging%20with%20the%20local%3F%20Quite%20logical!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20students%20are%20customers%20with%20consumerist%20entitlements%2C%20a%20degree%20logically%20turns%20into%20a%20commodity.%20The%20period%20for%20choosing%20and%20dropping%20courses%20is%20called%20%E2%80%98shopping%20week%E2%80%99.%20Campus-lifestyle%20becomes%20a%20register%20of%20exclusionary%20tendencies%20and%20strategic-distinction.%20Education%20gets%20subsumed%20under%20the%20all-pervasive%20claim%20of%20being%20world-class.%20And%20the%20society%20%E2%80%93%20at%20large%E2%80%93%20aims%20to%20out-class%20and%20exclude%20the%20%E2%80%98other%E2%80%99%20that%20cannot%20afford.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ESreedeep%20is%20a%20Sociologist%20with%20Shiv%20Nadar%20University%20and%20is%20the%20author%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3EConsumerist%20Encounters%20(2020)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702895447000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18152508%2FRight-to-Education.-Karan-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fcaste-class-and-exclusivity-inside-indias-private-universities%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Loaded%20with%20faculty%20with%20foreign%20PhDs%2C%20these%20institutions%20promise%20credibility%20that%20the%20rapidly%20declining%20public%20universities%20have%20lost.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fcaste-class-and-exclusivity-insid