%20skin%20flare-ups%20and%20anaphylaxis%20shock.%20Beth%20Tsangarides%20said%20that%20her%20body%20reacts%20to%20%26quot%3Beverything%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20feels%20like%20she's%20being%20%26quot%3Bburned%20alive%26quot%3B%20after%20laughing%2C%20crying%20or%20smelling%20spices.%20Ms%20Tsangarides%20revealed%20she%20has%20suffered%20from%20the%20chronic%20illness%20since%20the%20age%20of%2015%20and%20says%20that%20doctors%20still%20consider%20her%20a%20%26quot%3Bmedical%20mystery.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Tsangarides%20faces%20challenges%20like%20mobility%20issues%2C%20fainting%2C%20and%20seizures%2C%20rendering%20her%20unable%20to%20work.%C2%A0Her%20partner%2C%2020-year-old%20Sasha%20Hay%2C%20fulfils%20the%20role%20of%20her%20full-time%20caregiver%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirror.co.uk%2Fnews%2Freal-life-stories%2Fim-allergic-myself-feels-like-31644500%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMirror%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Medical%20professionals%20have%20labelled%20her%20a%20'medical%20mystery%2C'%20expressing%20their%20bewilderment%20at%20the%20unique%20nature%20of%20her%20condition.%20She%20humorously%20acknowledges%20family%20jokes%20about%20being%20%26quot%3Ballergic%20to%20herself%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20her%20body's%20unusual%20reactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCyyDlA7i0zj%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCyyDlA7i0zj%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCyyDlA7i0zj%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCyyDlA7i0zj%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Beth%20Tsangarides%20(%40bethtsangarides)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenging%20journey%20began%20five%20years%20ago%20when%20she%20noticed%20a%20rash%20on%20her%20face.%20Subsequently%2C%20her%20overall%20health%20declined%2C%20with%20issues%20in%20her%20bowels%20and%20kidneys.%20Ms%20Tsangarides%20shares%20that%20a%20range%20of%20emotions%2C%20from%20laughter%20to%20tears%2C%20can%20trigger%20skin%20flare-ups%2C%20describing%20the%20sensation%20as%20akin%20to%20feeling%20%26quot%3Bburned%20alive%26quot%3B%20with%20excruciating%20pain.%20At%20the%20age%20of%2018%2C%20she%20received%20a%20diagnosis%20of%20postural%20tachycardia%20syndrome%20(PoTS)%2C%20characterized%20by%20an%20abnormal%20increase%20in%20heart%20rate%20upon%20standing.%20Currently%2C%20she%20is%20undergoing%20testing%20to%20identify%20the%20specific%20cause%20of%20her%20skin-related%20challenges.%20According%20to%20the%20NHS%2C%20common%20PoTS%20symptoms%20include%20dizziness%2C%20fainting%2C%20palpitations%2C%20and%20chest%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20I%20describe%20it%20is%20like%20someone%20being%20burnt%20in%20a%20fire%20or%20an%20acid%20attack.%20For%20some%20people%20that's%20what%20it%20looks%20like%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%20%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20what%20I%20do%2C%20even%20if%20someone%20else%20with%20PoTS%20can%20do%20something%2C%20my%20body%20reacts%20differently%20to%20it.%26quot%3B%20Beth%20is%20most%20sensitive%20to%20food%20and%20says%20she%20lives%20%26quot%3Bin%20a%20bubble%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20airborne%20allergies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I'm%20around%20the%20smells%20of%20certain%20spices%20and%20herbs%20or%20something%20very%20strong%20smell%2C%20it%20can%20cause%20me%20to%20stop%20breathing%20and%20have%20a%20severe%20reaction%20on%20my%20face.%20I'm%20very%20limited%20in%20what%20I%20can%20eat%20and%20it's%20scary%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BPasta%20is%20my%20best%20friend%20because%20it's%20the%20only%20thing%20I've%20never%20reacted%20to.%20I%20try%20to%20stick%20to%20plain%20things%20like%20plain%20chicken%20nuggets.%20I%20don't%20go%20out%20to%20eat.%20If%20I%20do%20it%20has%20to%20be%20pre-planned%20and%20after%20speaking%20to%20the%20chef.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shared%20that%20while%20growing%20up%20she%20felt%20lonely%20and%20%26quot%3Bdidn't%20make%20many%20friends%26quot%3B%20at%20school.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20isolated%20in%20a%20room%20because%20we%20didn't%20know%20what%20I%20would%20react%20to%2C%20so%20I%20would%20be%20in%20the%20first%20aid%20room%20and%20constantly%20being%20checked%20on%20by%20teachers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explained.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20would%20look%20at%20me%20through%20the%20window%20and%20rumours%20were%20going%20around%20about%20what%20was%20wrong%20with%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20did%20affect%20my%20confidence%20at%20an%20early%20age.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20go%20out...%20I%20would%20get%20comments%20from%20people%20at%20school%20saying%20'pizza%20face'%20and%20'tomato%20face'.%20They%20used%20to%20affect%20me%20but%20now%20I%20just%20laugh.%26quot%3B%20Beth%20said%20her%20condition%20has%20changed%20her%20mentally.%20%26quot%3BI'll%20never%20know%20who%20I%20would've%20been%20without%20all%20of%20this.%20That's%20something%20I%20think%20about%20every%20day%2C%20'What%20would%20I%20be%20doing%20right%20now%20if%20I%20hadn't%20gotten%20ill%3F'%26quot%3B%20she%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shared%20that%20she%20has%20now%20started%20using%20make-up%20and%20feels%20more%20confident%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20wore%20make-up%20as%20a%20teenager%20a%20lot.%20I%20had%20really%20bad%20acne%20and%20I%20used%20to%20love%20doing%20make-up%20looks%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20my%20skin%20first%20flared%20I%20knew%20I%20would%20never%20be%20able%20to%20put%20make-up%20on%20it%20again.%20My%20doctors%20just%20told%20me%20to%20avoid%20it%20completely%20because%20there's%20a%20risk%20of%20infection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20just%20brave%20enough%20to%20try%20it%20again%20and%20I%20think%20that's%20all%20to%20do%20with%20the%20confidence%20I've%20gained%20over%20the%20last%20year.%20I%20did%20so%20much%20research%20into%20it%20and%20looked%20at%20every%20ingredient%20in%20everything.%20I%20was%20so%20happy%20when%20I%20realised%20it%20wasn't%20hurting%20and%20I%20wasn't%20flaring.%20It%20was%20crazy.%20It%20was%20so%20weird%20seeing%20my%20skin%20so%20smooth%20and%20without%20any%20imperfections%20or%20scarring.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20%3Cem%3EMirror%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20brought%20tears%20to%20my%20eyes%20because%20it%20wasn't%20even%20the%20fact%20I%20wanted%20to%20cover%20my%20skin%2C%20just%20the%20feeling%20of%20make-up%20on%20my%20skin%20felt%20so%20refreshing%20and%20like%20I%20was%20a%20new%20person.%20My%20partner%20was%20in%20shock.%20She's%20never%20seen%20me%20in%20make-up%20and%20she%20doesn't%20see%20make-up%20as%20a%20big%20thing%20or%20wear%20it%20herself.%20She%20did%20look%20at%20me%20and%20then%20looked%20away%20because%20she%20thought%20I%20was%20a%20different%20person.%20She%20couldn't%20believe%20how%20different%20I%20looked.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702893240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fa4slp6p8_beth-tsangarides_625x300_18_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fit-feels-like-im-burning-us-woman-describes-her-chronic-illness-4696318%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ms%20Tsangarides%20faces%20challenges%20like%20mobility%20issues%2C%20fainting%2C%20and%20seizures%2C%20rendering%20her%20unable%20to%20work.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fit-feels-like-im-burning-us-woman-describes-her-chronic-illness-4696318%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fit-feels-like-im-burning-us-woman-describes-her-chronic-illness-4696318%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fit-feels-like-im-burning-us-woman-describes-her-chronic-illness-4696318%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kotak%20Mahindra%20appoints%20Eli%20Leenaars%20as%20additional%20and%20independent%20director%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702892691000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-12%2F18%2Ffull%2F1702891850-8048.JPG%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fkotak-mahindra-appoints-eli-leenaars-as-additional-and-independent-director-123121800515_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%2035%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20financial%20sector%2C%20Eli%20Leenaars'%20new%20appointment%20will%20take%20effect%20from%20January%201%2C%202024%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fkotak