-news%2Fthis-chinese-game-won-awards-from-apple-google-and-the-oscars-of-gaming-in-2023%2Farticleshow%2F106087527.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IPL%202024%20Auction%3A%20From%20RCB%20To%20CSK%2C%20Players%2010%20Teams%20Are%20Likely%20To%20Sign%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20mini%20auctions%20of%20IPL%20have%20always%20been%20intriguing%20because%20of%20high%20demand-short%20supply%20ratio%20of%20players%2C%20especially%2C%20quality%20Indian%20talent.%20There%20could%20be%20some%20eye-popping%20deals%20for%20players%2C%20who%20would%20have%20struggled%20otherwise%20to%20attract%20attention%20in%20the%20mega%20auction.%20Here%20is%20a%20look%20at%20possible%20auction%20strategy%20for%20teams%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1)%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Purse%20Left%3A%20Rs%2031.4%20crore%20Potential%20Players%20of%20Interest%3A%20Shardul%20Thakur%2C%20Manish%20Pandey%2C%20Josh%20Hazlewood%20Shardul%20Thakur%20was%20earlier%20with%20the%20CSK%20and%20is%20a%20seasoned%20Indian%20campaigner%2C%20who%20can%20bowl%20at%20death%20and%20chance%20his%20arms%20coming%20in%20at%20No.%208.%20CSK%20could%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%20crore%20and%20upwards%20for%20Shardul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20would%20also%20look%20at%20an%20Indian%20batter%20to%20replace%20Ambati%20Rayudu%20and%20may%20look%20at%20veteran%20Manish%20Pandey%20for%20bargain%20buy%20as%20there%20aren't%20too%20many%20experienced%20Indians%20listed%20in%20the%20auction%20roster.%20If%20they%20want%20to%20bolster%20pace%20department%20then%20Josh%20Hazlewood%20is%20an%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2)%20Delhi%20Capitals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Purse%20Left%3A%20Rs%2028.95%20crore%20Potential%20Players%20of%20Interest%3A%20Priyansh%20Arya%2C%20Harshal%20Patel%2C%20Shardul%20Thakur%2C%20Jos%20Inglis%2C%20Wanindu%20Hasaranga%20Delhi%20Capitals'%20weakest%20link%20is%20their%20Indian%20collection%20of%20batters%20and%20poor%20is%20under