2%3A%22%26quot%3BListen%20Draupadi...%26quot%3B%3A%20High%20Court%20Cites%20Poem%20In%20Woman%20Paraded%20Naked%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20today%20invoked%20the%20mythological%20character%20Draupadi%20from%20the%20Mahabharata%20while%20hearing%20the%20case%20of%20assault%20on%20a%20woman%20in%20Belagavi%20where%20the%20victim%20was%20assaulted%2C%20paraded%20naked%2C%20and%20tied%20to%20an%20electric%20pole%20after%20her%20son%20eloped%20with%20a%20girl%20promised%20to%20someone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20expressed%20dismay%20over%20the%20incident%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BSo%20many%20bystanders%2C%20but%20nobody%20did%20anything.%20It%20is%20collective%20cowardice%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20addressed.%20The%20police%20are%20not%20of%20British%20Raj.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20highlighted%20the%20need%20for%20collective%20responsibility%20in%20preventing%20such%20atrocities.%20%C2%A0The%20Chief%20Justice%20referred%20to%20the%20present%20era%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bage%20of%20Duryodhanas%20and%20Dushasanas%2C%26quot%3B%20alluding%20to%20characters%20from%20the%20Mahabharata%20who%20symbolise%20injustice%20and%20malice.%20The%20court%20invoked%20a%20powerful%20poem%2C%20urging%20action%3A%20%26quot%3BListen%20Draupadi!%20Pick%20up%20your%20weapons%3B%20now%20Govind%20will%20not%20come.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poem%20is%20often%20used%20metaphorically%20to%20encourage%20the%20oppressed%20to%20rise%20and%20fight%20for%20justice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshok%2C%2024%2C%20and%20Priyanka%2C%2018%2C%20belong%20to%20the%20same%20community%20and%20were%20in%20love%2C%20police%20said.%20Around%2012%3A30%20pm%20last%20Monday%2C%20they%20left%20the%20village.%20Angered%20by%20this%2C%20Priyanka's%20parents%20and%20relatives%20barged%20into%20his%20house%2C%20assaulted%20and%20dragged%20her%2042-year-old%20mother%20out%20before%20parading%20her%20naked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrawing%20parallels%20with%20historical%20precedent%2C%20the%20court%20cited%20an%20incident%20during%20Former%20Governor-General%20of%20India%20Lord%20William%20Bentinck's%20period%2C%20where%20the%20entire%20village%20was%20made%20to%20pay%20for%20a%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20village%20people%20should%20be%20made%20responsible.%20Those%20who%20serve%20lip%20service%20are%20not%20good%20for%20us.%20there%20is%20a%20counter-argument%20that%20if%20I%20have%20not%20done%20anything%20why%20punish%20me%3F%20But%20being%20a%20mute%20spectator...somebody%20could%20have%20tried%20to%20stop%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20has%20directed%20the%20Criminal%20Investigation%20Department%20(CID)%20to%20probe%20the%20incident.%20Considering%20the%20trauma%20she%20is%20undergoing%2C%20the%20High%20Court%20in%20an%20earlier%20hearing%20said%20the%20continuous%20stream%20of%20people%20visiting%20her%20should%20be%20restricted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702891200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-02%2F7nrvsosc_karnataka-high-court-650_625x300_22_February_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flisten-draupadi-high-court-cites-poem-in-woman-paraded-naked-case-4696125%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20today%20invoked%20the%20mythological%20character%20Draupadi%20from%20the%20Mahabharata%20while%20hearing%20the%20case%20of%20assault%20on%20a%20woman%20in%20Belagavi%20where%20the%20victim%20was%20assaulted%2C%20paraded%20naked%2C%20and%20tied%20to%20an%20electric%20pole%20after%20her%20son%20eloped.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flisten-draupadi-high-court-cites-poem-in-woman-paraded-naked-case-4696125%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flisten-draupadi-high-court-cites-poem-in-woman-paraded-naked-case-4696125%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flisten-draupadi-high-court-cites-poem-in-woman-paraded-naked-case-4696125%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Inflationary%20Tax%E2%80%99%20on%20Its%20Poor%20Is%20Guided%20by%20Corporate%20Greed%20and%20Price%20Gouging%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F16122623%2FRussian-oil-tankers-low.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20column%20is%20based%20on%20ideas%20deliberated%20in%20the%C2%A0%20International%20Economics%20Association%20(IEA)%20conference%20held%20at%20Medellin%2C%20Colombia%20from%2011%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E-16%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20December.%20See%20details%20on%20IEA%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fieawc2023.org%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ehere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20can%20inflation%20levels%20persistently%20remain%20high%20in%20a%20country%20when%20the%20consumption%20demand%20level%20amongst%20different%20income%20groups%20has%20remained%20low%20for%20a%20longer%20duration%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20the%20question%20raised%20to%20Economist%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIsabellaMWeber%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIsabella%20M.%20Weber%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20recently%20listed%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2Fcollection%2Ftime100-next-2023%2F6308509%2Fisabella-weber%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETimes100%20list%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20most%20influential%20people%2C%20during%20the%20ongoing%20International%20Economic%20Association%20(IEA)%20summit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWeber%E2%80%99s%20work%20in%20the%20US%20and%20EU%20context%20has%20explained%20%E2%80%98price%20gouging%E2%80%99%2C%20anchored%20by%20corporate%20greed%2C%20as%20a%20vital%20causative%20factor%20influencing%20higher%20(inflationary)%20prices%20across%20sectors-calling%20this%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faustraliainstitute.org.au%2Fevent%2Fthe-economics-and-politics-of-sellers-inflation-with-isabella-weber%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eseller%E2%80%99s%20inflation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECompanies%2C%20particularly%20in%20oligopolistic%20market%20conditions%20(markets%20where%20few%20firms%2Fcorporate%20companies%20control%20the%20market%20share%20of%20a%20commodity)%20tend%20to%20keep%20prices%20high%20to%20earn%20abnormal%20profits%2C%20especially%20in%20times%20of%20conflict%2C%20crisis%20or%20emergencies%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98greed%E2%80%99%20underlines%20the%20motivation%20for%20artificially%20producing%20inflation%2C%20acting%20as%20a%20tax%20on%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20and%20poor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIs%20this%20true%20for%20all%20inflationary%20expectations%2Ftrends%20being%20observed%20across%20the%20globe%20now%3F%20Weber%20and%20other%20experts%20studying%20recent%20inflationary%20trends%20from%20a%20supply-side%20perspective%20agree.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20oil%20companies%20were%20making%20abnormal%20profits%20from%20volatile%20oil%20prices%20in%20Europe%2C%20one%20of%20the%20measures%20adopted%20by%20the%20European%20Union%20was%20to%20impose%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewindfall%20profit%20tax%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20the%20energy%20providers%20%E2%80%93%20to%20correct%20the%20abnormal%20rise%20of%20incomes%20experienced%20by%20such%20companies%20and%20give%20relief%20to%20the%20consumers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFuel%20price-anchored%20supply-side%20inflation%20cascades%20into%20higher%20food-price%20inflation%20(particularly%20in%20developing%20countries%20like%20India)%2C%20as%20explained%20by%20this%20author%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-modi-government-must-answer-for-its-exploitative-fuel-price-policy%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20a%20recent%20study%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20Indian%20scenario%20though%2C%20instead%20of%20imposing%20any%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ewindfall%20profit%20tax%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20profiteering%20firms%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-modi-government-must-answer-for-its-exploitative-fuel-price-policy%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENarendra%20Modi%20government%20did%20the%20opposite%20by%20closely%20colluding%20with%20oil%20companies%20to%20profit%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20any%20potential%20gains%20made%20from%20cheaper%20oil%20imports%20(from%20Russia).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20own%20tryst%20with%20%E2%80%98seller%E2%80%99s%20inflation%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFood%20prices%20in%20India%20have%20remained%20high%20for%20a%20few%20years%20now.%20Much%20of%20this%20is%20usually%20explained%20by%20seasonal%2C%20distributive%20factors%20where%20agri-based%20pricing%20mechanisms%20are%20influenced%20by%20a%20volatile%20monsoon%20trend%20and%20an%20urban%20consumer%20bias%20often%20results%20in%20higher%20food%20inflation%20trends.%20However%2C%20the%20longevity%20of%20this%20wave%20of%20food%20inflation-supported%20by%20high%20fuel%20prices%20and%20retail%20firm-based%20price%20gouging%20%E2%80%93%20in%20a%20weak%20urban%20and%20rural%20consumption%20demand%20environment%20%E2%80%93%20has%20evidence%20from%20Isabella%E2%80%99s%20seller%E2%80%99s%20inflation%20theory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20BJP%20came%20into%20power%2C%20India%20has%20seen%20its%20import%20demand%20for%20oil%20grow%20steadily%2C%20with%20the%20import%20of%20crude%20oil%20and%20other%20petroleum%20products%20nearly%20tripling%20in%20volume%20between%202014%20and%202022.%20This%20growing%20demand%20for%20energy%20has%20also%20been%20observed%20in%20the%20composition%20of%20merchandise%20imports%20between%20the%20same%20range%2C%20with%20imports%20of%20oil%20products%20nearly%20doubling%20in%20value%20from%20Rs%2078%2C281%20crores%20in%20April%202014%20to%20Rs.%20168%2C226%20crores%20in%20July%202022.%20See%20below.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18142759%2Fimage7.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18142759%2Fimage7.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18142759%2Fimage7-300x218.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18142759%2Fimage7-1024x744.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689646%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22872%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20CNES-InfoSphere%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20this%20rising%20import%20bill%20may%20present%20an%20issue%20for%20any%20government%2C%20through%20imposing%20taxes%2C%20the%20government%20has%20been%20able%20to%20contain%20the%20prices%20of%20oil%20products%20such%20as%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20in%20a%20narrow%20band.%20The%20avenue%20of%20tax%20component%20in%20the%20prices%20of%20motor%20spirits%20has%20been%20a%20major%20source%20of%20revenue%20for%20the%20Union%20government.%20Taxes%20on%20oil%20and%20petroleum%20products%20form%20a%20major%20part%20of%20the%20retail%20prices%20borne%20by%20the%20consumers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18142918%2Fimage1.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18142918%2Fimage1.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18142918%2Fimage1-300x218.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18142918%2Fimage1-1024x745.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689647%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22873%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20CNES-InfoSphere%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20government%20keeps%20a%20fixed%20rate%20of%20excise%20duties%20on%20the%20base%20price%20of%20petrol%20and%20diesel%2C%20which%20has%20contributed%20to%20an%20increasing%20dependence%20on%20the%20revenues%20from%20such%20duties.%20Of%20the%20total%20tax%20contribution%20from%20the%20petroleum%20sector%20to%20the%20Exchequer%2C%20excise%20duties%20levied%20from%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20have%20accounted%20for%20nearly%2075-90%25%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%20(for%20state%20governments%2C%20VAT%20from%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20has%20accounted%20for%2085-95%25%20during%20the%20same%20period).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18143013%2Fimage2.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18143013%2Fimage2.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18143013%2Fimage2-300x218.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18143013%2Fimage2-1024x745.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689648%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22873%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20CNES-InfoSphere%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18143027%2Fimage4.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18143027%2Fimage4.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18143027%2Fimage4-300x218.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18143027%2Fimage4-1024x745.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689649%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22873%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20CNES-InfoSphere%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWeber%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIsabellaMWeber%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eargues%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20such%20acts%20of%20keeping%20prices%20higher%20for%20higher%20profitability%20aren%E2%80%99t%20unique%20to%20the%20Indian%20scenario.%20The%20US%20too%20has%20seen%20it%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20and%20so%20have%20other%20countries%20in%20Europe%2C%20where%20market%20power%20is%20unevenly%20tilted%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98few%E2%80%99%20companies.%20Pre-existing%20inequities%20in%20market%20conditions%20have%20incentivised%20price%20gouging%20across%20sectors%20-from%20oil%20to%20retail.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECompanies%20use%20%