3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20prices%20of%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20have%20hovered%20around%20Rs%20100%20despite%20the%20cut%20in%20excise%20duties%2C%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20how%20the%20oncoming%20production%20cut%20will%20be%20managed%20by%20the%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18143434%2Fimage6.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18143434%2Fimage6.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18143434%2Fimage6-300x218.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18143434%2Fimage6-1024x745.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689651%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22873%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20CNES-InfoSphere%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELeading%20up%20to%20the%20general%20elections%20of%202024%2C%20OPEC%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20cut%20production%20would%20certainly%20not%20bode%20well%20for%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20fuel%20import%20bill.%20Also%2C%20with%20the%20dollar%20exchange%20rate%20already%20at%20a%20record%20high%20despite%20RBI%20intervention%2C%20and%20inflation%20already%20high%2C%20the%20incoming%20rise%20in%20fuel%20costs%20is%20surely%20expected%20to%20add%20to%20the%20fire.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20spinoff%20in%20the%20narrative%20projected%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20in%20managing%20the%20headline-fuel%20inflation%20is%20also%20interesting.%20It%20first%20allows%20the%20price%20of%20retail%20petrol%20and%20diesel%2C%20much%20like%20LPG%2C%20to%20scale%20up%20%E2%80%93%20citing%20%E2%80%98e