)%20profited%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20poor%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20chart%20below%20provides%20a%20mapping%20between%20CPI-Oil%20price%20numbers%20across%20major%20cities%20%E2%80%93%20engines%20of%20urban%20growth%20%E2%80%93%20across%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20strong%20case%20for%20the%20government%20and%20particularly%20the%20opposition%20to%20recognise%20how%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20its%20allied%20group%20of%20companies%20profited%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20poor%20by%20imposing%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fopinion%2Findias-soaring-inflation-is-an-invisible-tax-on-the-poor%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98inflation%20tax%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cspan%3E%20This%20was%20not%20just%20motivated%20by%20corporate%20greed%20in%20the%20private%20sector%2C%20but%20collusively%20supported%20by%20profit-seeking%2C%20incumbent%20government%20that%20did%20nothing%20to%20recognize%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20amidst%20a%20bad%20agricultural%20harvest%20season%20and%20rising%20protectionism%20across%20the%20globe%2C%20as%20input%20prices%20go%20up%20and%20food%20inflation%20(with%20prices%20of%20wheat%2C%20pulses%2C%20cereals%20etc.)%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20remain%20higher%20with%20a%20combined%20weight%20of%20other%20distributive%20%E2%80%98supply%20side%E2%80%99%20reasons%20playing%20a%20role%20too.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F996718%2Fif-india-aims-to-contain-inflation-it-must-diagnose-the-problem-right%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EStandard%20monetary%20policy%20toolkit%20measures%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20address%20these%20concerns%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20unless%20the%20government%20is%20made%20to%20recognise%20its%20folly%2C%20and%20perhaps%20be%20strongly%20nudged%20into%20using%20fiscal%20policy%20instruments%20to%20keep%20inflationary%20food%20prices%20lo