to%20the%20venue%20and%20paid%20the%20outstanding%20amount%2C%20which%20was%20%2412%2C426%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithin%20the%20last%20week%2C%20ten%20guests%2C%20who%20had%20previously%20RSVP'd%2C%20said%20that%20they%20were%20coming%20and%20have%20now%20cancelled%20citing%20that%20it's%20too%20expensive%20for%20them%20to%20travel%20interstate%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%20The%20woman%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20she%20was%20essentially%20losing%20out%20on%20%241%2C336%20if%20she%20didn't%20%26quot%3Bscramble%20to%20cover%20their%20seats.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20it%20reasonable%20to%20request%20that%20they%20cover%20these%20costs%20themselves%3F%26quot%3B%20The%20bride%20also%20added%20that%20formal%20invites%20were%20sent%20out%20in%20January%20this%20year%2C%20with%20the%20majority%20of%20attendees%20responding%20by%20July.%20Not%20only%20this%2C%20the%20guests%20were%20given%20a%20%26quot%3BSave%20the%20Date%26quot%3B%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years%20prior.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20shared%20the%20messages%20received%20by%20the%20people%20who%20cancelled%20the%20wedding.%20%26quot%3BSo%20sorry%2C%20I%20know%20we%20RSVP'd%20yes%20and%20the%20wedding%20is%20next%20week%20but%20we%20just%20can't%20afford%20to%20travel%20interstate%20at%20the%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20text%20message%20read.%20%26quot%3BHope%20you%20understand%2C%20would%20love%20to%20have%20been%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20podcast's%20audience%20was%20quick%20to%20pick%20sides%2C%20with%20many%20saying%20that%20the%20guests%20should%20pay%20for%20their%20late%20cancellations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20books%20flights%20for%20an%20interstate%20wedding%20the%20week%20prior.%20The%20guest%20is%20100%25%20at%20fault%20here%20and%20is%20not%20a%20nice%20friend%20for%20doing%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20listener%20weighed%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26