-towns-along-australias-great-barrier-reef-13033257%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmore-than-300-evacuated-after-flooding-hits-towns-along-australias-great-barrier-reef-13033257%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chileans%20Vote%20Against%20New%20Constitution%20Drafted%20by%20Far-Right%20Party%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18105632%2Ffrancisco-kemeny-IDWGW0tlB18-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Chileans%20voted%20down%20a%20new%20conservative%20constitution%2C%20drafted%20by%20a%20far-right%20party%2C%20in%20a%20referendum%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20draft%20was%20to%20replace%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20dictatorship-era%C2%A0text.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%2099.65%25%20of%20ballot%20boxes%20tallied%2C%20a%20total%20of%2055.76%25%20Chileans%20rejected%20the%20new%20text%20while%2044.24%25%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20had%20argued%20that%20this%20draft%20extended%20some%20of%20the%20problems%20in%20the%20Pinochet-era%20document%2C%20including%20in%20provisions%20on%20abortion%20and%20same-sex%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EBREAKING%20%F0%9F%87%A8%F0%9F%87%B1%20Chile%E2%80%99s%20new%20draft%20constitution%20%E2%80%94%20which%20threatened%20to%20enshrine%20an%20extremist%20neoliberal%20model%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20constitution%2C%20extending%20Pinochet%E2%80%99s%20original%20vision%20to%20include%20provisions%20against%20abortion%20and%20same-sex%20marriage%20%E2%80%94%20has%20been%20overwhelmingly%20rejected.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fk74Fm2p0rb%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fk74Fm2p0rb%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20David%20Adler%20(%40davidrkadler)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdavidrkadler%2Fstatus%2F1736536277099430210%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2017%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20country%20got%20polarised%2C%20divided%2C%E2%80%9D%20President%20Gabriel%20Boric%20said%20during%20a%20televised%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%C2%A0result%20shows%20the%20process%20%E2%80%9Cdidn%E2%80%99t%20channel%20the%20hopes%20of%20having%20a%20new%20constitution%20written%20by%20everyone.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20draft%20constitution%20was%20written%20by%20the%20far-right%20Republican%20Party%2C%20and%20it%20was%20the%20second%20attempt%20to%20replace%20the%20constitution%20written%20under%20military%20dictator%20Augusto%20Pinochet%20after%20Chileans%20also%20voted%20down%20a%20progressive%20text%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20failed%20in%20the%20effort%20to%20convince%20Chileans%20that%20this%20would%20be%20a%20better%20constitution%20than%20the%20existing%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Republican%20leader%20Jose%20Antonio%20Kast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtests%20sparked%20calls%20for%20change%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vote%20for%20potential%20reform%C2%A0came%C2%A0after%C2%A0large-scale%2C%20passionate%20and%20occasionally%C2%A0violent%20protests%20against%20inequality%20gripped%20the%20South%20American%20country%C2%A0in%202019%2C%20led%20primarily%20by%20young%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unrest%C2%A0kicked%20off%20a%20process%20to%20scrap%20the%20constitution%20%E2%80%94%20a%20move%20supported%20by%2080%25%20of%20voters%20in%20a%202020%20referendum%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0which%20had%20its%20roots%20in%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20bloody%2017-year%20military%20dictatorship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20existing%20constitution%20from%201980%20was%20blamed%20for%20allowing%20large%20corporations%20and%20the%20elites%20to%20enrich%20themselves%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20surge%20in%20street%20protests%C2%A0also%20resulted%20in%20the%20election%20of%20the%20young%2C%20leftist%C2%A0Boric%20who%20had%20previously%20been%20a%20student%20activist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20years%20on%20from%20those%C2%A0protests%2C%20however%2C%C2%A0enthusiasm%20has%20waned%2C%20largely%20due%20to%C2%A0the%20pandemic%2C%20inflation%20and%20economic%20stagnation%2C%C2%A0say%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20progressive%20proposal%20in%202022%20included%20stronger%20protections%20for%20Indigenous%20rights%2C%20proposals%20to%20protect%20natural%20resources%20such%20as%20water%2C%C2%A0a%20requirement%20for%20women%20to%20hold%20at%20least%20half%20of%20positions%20in%20public%20institutions%2C%20and%20the%20right%20to%20abortion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conservative%20text%20that%20the%20public%20voted%20on%20over%20the%20weekend%20instead%20enshrined%20the%20right%20to%20life%20from%20the%20moment%20of%20conception%20and%20allowed%20for%20the%20expedited%20deportation%20of%20undocumented%20migrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaudia%20Heiss%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Chile%20said%20the%20latest%20rewrite%C2%A0%E2%80%9Cfalls%20between%20the%201980%20constitution%20and%20one%20even%20more%20to%20the%20right.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReferendum%20outcome%20expected%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20draft%C2%A0was%20overseen%20by%20the%20far-right%20opposition%20Republican%20Party%20after%20citizens%20voted%20against%C2%A0a%20progressive%20version%C2%A0in%20September%202022%20that%20attempted%20to%20enshrine%20environmental%20protections%20and%20the%20right%20to%20elective%20abortion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHad%20the%20new%20text%20been%20approved%2C%20it%20could%20have%20further%20hindered%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fgabriel-boric-chiles-democracy-still-under-construction%2Fa-66774928%5C%22%3EPresident%20Boric%E2%80%99s%20manifesto%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20progressive%20tax%20and%20pension%20reforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoric%20said%20he%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20pursue%20a%20third%20attempt%20to%20rewrite%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20the%20citizenry%20is%20demanding%20is%20a%20better%20capacity%20for%20dialogue%2C%20of%20consensus%2C%20but%20most%20of%20all%20action%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fchile-rejects-second-attempt-to-renew-constitution%2Fa-67749225%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20from%3C%2Fem%3E%20DW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702877531000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18105632%2Ffrancisco-kemeny-IDWGW0tlB18-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fchileans-vote-against-new-constitution-drafted-by-far-right-party%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Critics%20had%20argued%20that%20this%20draft%20extended%20some%20of%20the%20problems%20in%20the%20existing%20Pinochet-era%20document%2C%20including%20in%20provisions%20on%20abortion%20and%20same-sex%20marriage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fchileans-vote-against-new-constitution-drafted-by-far-right-party%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chileans%20vote%20not%20to%20replace%20Pinochet-era%20constitution%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702877506000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F16BF9%2Fproduction%2F_132077139_ba450568bd8807740e3dd00f619eb65d28dd53d10_0_5500_36681000x667.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-67745456%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20new%20constitution%20would%20have%20affected%20areas%20including%20abortions%2C%20strike%20action%20and%20indigenous%20rights.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-67745456%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-