front%20of%20the%20Calicut%20University%20guest%20house%20where%20he%20was%20staying%2C%20the%20governor%20has%20decided%20that%20this%20was%20done%20at%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbehest%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20state%20chief%20minister%20and%20went%20as%20far%20as%20to%20call%20it%20an%20attempt%20to%20%E2%80%9Cprecipitate%20the%20breakdown%20of%20constitutional%20machinery%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Students%E2%80%99%20Federation%20of%20India%2C%20the%20student%20wing%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%2C%20had%20earlier%20announced%20that%20Khan%20would%20not%20be%20allowed%20into%20university%20spaces%20in%20the%20state%20because%20of%20his%20allegedly%20undemocratic%20actions.%20Khan%20challenged%20this%20by%20going%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20Calicut%20University%20guest%20house%20on%20Saturday%2C%20prompting%20the%20students%20to%20use%20banners%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20their%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20banners%20accused%20Khan%20of%20doing%20whatever%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20wants%20and%20undermining%20the%20state%20government.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fkerala-governor-on-poster-row-in-university-cant-happen-without-cms-order-101702832979234.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20also%20called%20him%20a%20%E2%80%9CSanghi%E2%80%9D%20(member%20of%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20(December%2017)%2C%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20issued%20a%20formal%20statement%20in%20which%20it%20blamed%20chief%20minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20for%20what%20had%20happened.%20%E2%80%9CHon%E2%80%99ble%C2%A0Governor%20Arif%20Mohammed%20Khan%20has%20taken%20a%20serious%20note%20of%20the%20action%20of%20the%20state%20police%2C%20on%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20in%20placing%20posters%20defamatory%20to%20the%20Governor%20in%20the%20campus%20of%20Calicut%20University.%20The%20black%20banners%20and