%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fkerala-governor-refers-seven-pending-bills-to-president-a-day-before-sc-set-to-hear-state-govt-plea%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20has%20intervened%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20say%20that%20it%20is%20not%20the%20role%20of%20the%20governor%20to%20come%20in%20the%20way%20of%20the%20law-making%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUniversities%20have%20been%20another%20site%20of%20tension%2C%20where%20the%20governor%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20misusing%20his%20position%20as%20chancellor%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fkerala-governor-removed-as-chancellor-of-kalamandalam-university%5C%22%3Echange%20the%20vice-chancellors%20of%20a%20number%20of%20universities%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20state%20government%20last%20year%20came%20out%20with%20an%20ordinance%20to%20replace%20the%20governor%20as%20the%20chancellor%20of%20the%20universities%20and%20appoint%20eminent%20academicians%20to%20that%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702868959000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03132819%2FF7m7Y5YaIAAeDNr.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkerala-governor-claims-banners-criticising-him-precipitate-the-breakdown-of-constitutional-machinery%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20banners%20accused%20Khan%20of%20doing%20whatever%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20wants%20and%20undermining%20the%20state%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkerala-governor-claims-banners-criticising-him-precipitate-the-breakdown-of-constitutional-machinery%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Car%20crashes%20into%20vehicle%20guarding%20President%20Biden's%20motorcade%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702868220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F1600x900%2Fskynews-secret-service-del