e-in-power-has-brought-a-shrinking-welfare-landscape-to-india%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20the%20fourth%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fif-there-was-political-will-indias-raging-cost-of-living-crisis-could-be-eased%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20and%20the%20fifth%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fa-decade-of-write-offs-how-the-govt-and-banks-failed-to-tackle-npas-and-helped-big-corporations%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAs%2520reported%2520in%2520The%2520Wire%2C%2525%2520of%2520the%2520write%252Doffs.%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Chr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20no%20money%2C%20moneylenders%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20wait.%20What%20should%20we%20do%3F%20We%20can%E2%80%99t%20even%20afford%20to%20take%20onions%20to%20the%20market.%20You%20are%20just%20thinking%20about%20yourself%2C%20Modi%20saheb.%20You%20must%20provide%20the%20guaranteed%20price%20for%20the%20produce%E2%80%A6%20The%20finance%20guys%20threaten%2C%20and%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3Epatpedhi%3Cem%3E%20(cooperative%20society)%20officers%20abuse.%20Who%20should%20we%20go%20for%20justice%3F%E2%80%A6%20Today%2C%20I%20am%20forced%20to%20commit%20suicide%20because%20of%20your%20inaction.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20were%20the%20words%20of%20Dashrath%20Lakshman%20Kedari%20before%20he%20died%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fpune%2Fmaharashtra-farmer-suicide-note-blaming-pm-modi-8159289%2F%5C%22%3Esuicide%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20in%20Pune%20district%20of%20Maharashtra.%20His%20is%20one%20among%20the%201%2C00%2C474%20suicides%20in%20the%20farming%20sector%20in%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20years%20(2014-2022)%2C%20as%20per%20the%20recently%20released%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncrb.gov.in%2Faccidental-deaths-suicides-in-india-year-wise.html%3Fyear%3D2022%26keyword%3D%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20amounts%20to%20nearly%2030%20suicides%20per%20day%20in%20these%20nine%20years.%20And%20yet%20we%20heard%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20claiming%20that%20no%20farmer%20has%20died%20under%20Modi%20by%20suicide.%20%E2%80%9CDid%20the%20opposition%20ever%20have%20a%20single%20discussion%20about%20farmers%E2%80%99%20suicides%20in%20the%20last%20eight%20years%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffact-check-bjp-mp-nishikant-dubey-farmer-suicides%5C%22%3Easked%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%2C%3Cem%3E%20it%20means%20farmers%20are%20not%20dying%20by%20suicide.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20of%20the%20kisan%2C%20like%20the%20jawan%20or%20say%20corruption%2C%20has%20been%20one%20of%20those%20emotive%20subjects%20that%20has%20a%20bearing%20on%20the%20moral%20compass%20of%20the%20nation.%20The%20noose%20around%20the%20neck%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eannadata%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20has%20generally%20been%20a%20subject%20that%20arouses%20sentiments.%20But%20sadly%20the%20revelations%20of%20the%20present%20NCRB%20report%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20have%20evoked%20any%20such%20moral%20outrage%20in%20the%20media%20or%20on%20primetime%20debates.%20This%20is%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20in%20the%20second%20term%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20the%20total%20farmer%20suicides%20increased%20in%20absolute%20numbers%20from%2010%2C281%20to%2011%2C290.%20Within%20this%2C%20the%20rise%20in%20the%20number%20of%20suicides%20among%20agricultural%20workers%20seems%20to%20be%20much%20sharper%2C%20from%204%2C324%20to%206%2C083%20i.e.%2041%25.%20Maharashtra%2C%20with%20the%20ill-fated%20regions%20of%20Vidharbha%20and%20Marathwada%2C%20yet%20again%20witnessed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fmore-than-2300-farmer-suicides-in-10-months-in-maharashtra%5C%22%3Eworst%3C%2Fa%3E%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C