E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJawzara%20used%20to%20employ%20members%20of%20five%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fpakistan-why-liberal-pashtuns-are-supporting-the-afghan-government%2Fa-58819365%5C%22%3EAfghan%20Pashtun%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0families%2C%20who%20fled%20their%20country%20after%20the%20Soviet%20invasion%20in%201979.%20Refugee%20women%20used%20to%20do%20chores%20in%20her%20house%20and%C2%A0men%20worked%20in%20fields%2C%20with%20the%20Pakistani%20woman%20and%20two%20of%20her%20sons%20supervising%20and%20helping%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20new%20generations%20in%20the%20small%20community%20born%20and%20raised%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20they%20tended%20to%20live%20on%20Jawzara%E2%80%99s%20farmland%20and%20be%20dependent%20on%20the%20their%20employer%20for%20food%2C%20health%20care%20and%20other%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20recent%20anti-immigrant%20clampdown%20has%20changed%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20undocumented%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fafghanistan%2Ft-18932080%5C%22%3EAfghans%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Pakistan%20were%20living%20in%20Balochistan%20and%20northwestern%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20provinces%20%E2%80%93%20both%20bordering%20Afghanistan%20%E2%80%93%20and%20never%20felt%20residency%20documents%20were%20necessary%2C%20with%20their%20lives%20limited%20to%20their%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Pakistani%20government%20declared%20the%20presence%20of%20undocumented%20migrants%20to%20be%20both%20a%20security%20and%20economic%20challenge.%20Hundreds%20of%20thousands%20have%20already%20been%20expelled%20or%20left%20on%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20despite%20Pakistani%20officials%20pledging%20that%202.3%20million%20legal%20Afghan%20migrants%20were%20free%20to%20remain%C2%A0as%20long%20as%20their%20papers%20are%20valid%2C%20more%20than%20a%20few%20documented%20migrants%20also%20returned%20to%20their%20home%20country.%20They%20feared%20that%20Pakistan%C2%A0would%20soon%20try%20to%20deport%20them%20as%20well%2C%20and%20warned%20that%20the%20authorities%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fpakistan-police-detain-afghans-as-deadline-expires%2Fa-67274175%5C%22%3Elook%20determined%20to%20send%20all%20Afghans%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20documented%20or%20undocumented%20%E2%80%93%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAfghan%20workers%2C%20Pakistani%20employees%20caught%20%E2%80%98off%20guard%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfghan%20labourers%20have%20a%20reputation%20of%20being%20cheap%2C%20skilled%20and%20hardworking.%20They%20are%20also%20in%20a%20vulnerable%20position%20due%20to%20their%20living%20on%20foreign%20soil.%20The%20mass%20exodus%20has%20now%20sparked%20labor%20shortages%20in%20sectors%20like%20agriculture%20and%20mining%20in%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20border%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COrders%20for%20%5Bundocumented%5D%20migrants%20to%20leave%20caught%20our%20Afghan%20workers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20us%2C%20off%20guard.%20Neither%20were%20they%20mentally%20prepared%20to%20go%20away%20on%20short%20notice%2C%20nor%20did%20we%20have%20any%20idea%20of%20what%20to%20do%20without%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jahangir%20Shah%2C%20who%20owns%20a%20coal%20mine%20in%20Balochistan%E2%80%99s%20Duki%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfghans%20make%20up%2060%25%20of%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20employees.%20The%20repatriation%20effort%2C%20according%20to%20the%20mine%20owner%2C%20forced%20him%20to%20briefly%20suspend%20mining%20operations.%C2%A0Even%20after%20the%20work%20was%20resumed%20with%20extended%20shifts%2C%20production%20was%20very%20slow%20due%20to%20labor%20shortages.%20Shah%20fears%20production%20targets%20will%C2%A0not%20be%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20bids%20to%20return%20to%20normal%20face%20challenges%2C%20especially%20the%20unavailability%20of%20skilled%20workers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20DW%2C%20adding%20that%20workers%20from%20other%20areas%20are%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20coming%20in%20despite%20offers%20of%20better%20payment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrouble%20for%20Afghanistan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPashtuns%20are%20the%20dominant%20ethnic%20group%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20with%20millions%20of%20them%20also%20living%20in%20Pakistan.%20Sardar%20Muhammad%20Shafiq%20Tareen%2C%20a%20Pashtun%20serving%20as%20a%20senator%20in%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Balochistan%2C%20warns%20that%20almost%2080%25%20of%20workers%20in%20the%20mines%20and%20farms%20across%20the%20province%20were%20Afghan%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exodus%20of%20Afghans%C2%A0will%20also%20stop%20remittances%20from%20Pakistan%20into%20Afghanistan%2C%20harming%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20economic%20development%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20war-ravaged%20country%20is%20already%20facing%20a%20massive%20crisis%20following%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftaliban%2Ft-17428121%5C%22%3Ethe%20Taliban%3C%2Fa%3E%20takeover%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETareen%20echoed%20the%20concerns%20of%20many%20activists%20and%20international%20organizations%2C%20noting%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fpakistan-tens-of-thousands-of-afghans-flee-amid-crackdown%2Fa-67282199%5C%22%3EAfghans%20were%20given%20very%20little%20time%20to%20return%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20their%20home%20country%C2%A0despite%20spending%20years%20or%20decades%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20border.%20Speaking%20with%20DW%2C%20he%20questioned%20the%20Pakistani%20government%20narrative%20that%20most%20departures%20were%20voluntary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Doom%20scenario%E2%80%99%20for%20local%20mining%20industry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarious%20political%20parties%20and%20trader%20associations%20have%20been%20protesting%20government%20policies%C2%A0since%20October%2020%20by%20staging%20a%20sit-in%C2%A0in%20the%20border%20town%20of%20Chaman.%20They%20have%20opposed%20visa%20restrictions%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20anti-migrant%20clampdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPir%20Muhammad%20Kakar%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Balochistan%20chapter%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Workers%E2%80%99%20Federation%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20more%20than%20half%20of%20Afghans%20working%20in%20the%20province%E2%80%99s%20mines%20had%20left%2C%20causing%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdoom%20scenario%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20local%20mining%20industry%2C%20the%20largest%20income%20generator%20for%20the%20province.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKakar%20said%20mine%20owners%20recently%20met%20caretaker%20Interior%20Minister%20Sarfraz%20Bugti%20%E2%80%94%20himself%20a%20Balochistan%20native%20%E2%80%94%20who%20pledged%20to%20ensure%20that%20Afghan%20mine%20workers%20aren%E2%80%99t%20unduly%20bothered.%20The%20minister%20also%20promised%20a%20proper%20policy%20to%20enable%20the%20workers%20to%20continue%20their%20employment%2C%20but%20this%20promise%20has%20yet%20to%20be%20fulfilled%2C%20according%20to%20Kakar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fpakistans-farms-mines-in-trouble-with-afghans-pushed-out%2Fa-67736498%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702819826000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04191718%2F49869773933_4581459b7d_k2.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistans-farms-mines-in-trouble-with-afghans-pushed-out%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Skilled%20Afghan%20workers%20are%20in%20short%20supply%20in%20Pakistan%20as%20the%20country%20continues%20its%20clampdown%20on%20illegal%20migrants.%20Farmers%20and%20mine%20owners%20are%20now%20paying%20the%20price.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistans-farms-mines-in-trouble-with-afghans-pushed-out%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Stolen%20Land%E2%80%99%3A%20Why%20Locals%20are%20Decrying%20a%20Private%20Real%20Estate%20Developer%E2%80%99s%20Quiet%20Expansion%20in%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17171641%2Fimage-1623.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKarachi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20the%20Kirthar%20area%20of%20the%20Jamshoro%20district%2C%20a%20young%20man%20named%20Imaan%20Ali%20found%20himself%20surrounded%20by%20a%20group%20of%20activists%20and%20journalists.%20He%20alleges%20that%20his%20piece%20of%20land%2C%20along%20with%20that%20of%20other%20villagers%2C%20has%20been%20stolen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20group%20of%20journalists%20and%20activists%20has%20witnessed%20the%20ongoing%20usurpation%20of%20land%20in%20Kirthar%20by%20Bahria%20Town%20%E2%80%93%20a%20private%20real%20estate%20developer%20%E2%80%93%20from%20its%20local%20inhabitants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20how%20your%20land%E2%80%99s%20possession%20was%20given%20to%20Bahria%20Town%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSome%20policemen%20and%20guards%20of%20Bahria%20Town%20spoke%20in%20a%20threatening%20manner%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20law%20empowers%20Bahria%20Town%20to%20claim%20possession%20of%20the%20land.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAli%20continues%20and%20asks%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20could%20they%20do%3F%20Even%20local%20influential%20persons%20have%20pressured%20us%20to%20not%20resist%20and%20accept%20what%20Bahria%20Town%20says.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAli%20and%20other%20villagers%20felt%20abandoned%2C%20unable%20to%20fight%20against%20the%20owner%20of%20Bahria%20Town%2C%20Malik%20Riaz%2C%20who%20enjoys%20powerful%20support%20from%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20Hafeez%20Baloch%2C%20an%20activist%20with%20Indigenous%20Rights%20Alliances%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftherisenews.com%2F2023%2F05%2F26%2Fhttps-therisenews-com-p4814%2F%5C%22%3Ehas%20been%20engaged%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20struggle%20against%20the%20land%20mafia%2C%20Bahria%20Town%2C%20and%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Defense%20Housing%20Authority.%20He%20has%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20Pakistan%20against%20Bahria%20Town%20to%20protect%20the%20Kirthar%20Mountain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20witnessing%20yourself%20that%20Bahria%20Town%20is%20stealing%20people%E2%80%99s%20land%20by%20claiming%20that%20the%20law%20allows%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20Villagers%20wanted%20to%20fight%2C%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20no%20politician%20dared%20to%20stand%20up%20against%20Bahria%20Town.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20people%20who%20have%20been%20living%20here%20for%20centuries%20are%20now%20being%20forced%20to%20evacuate%20as%20if%20the%20land%20never%20belonged%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Malir%20district%20is%20a%20cradle%20of%20culture%20and%20bears%20a%20history%20that%20illustrates%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20place%2C%20along%20with%20the%20old%20pathways%20connecting%20it%20to%20other%20districts.%20The%20land%20speaks%20in%20silence%20through%20its%20beauty%20and%20mountains.%20However%2C%20now%2C%20land%20grabbers%20and%20real%20estate%20tycoons%20are%20erasing%20such%20beauty.%20The%20interests%20of%20a%20few%20have%20changed%20everything%20%E2%80%93%20once%2C%20villagers%20could%20not%20climb%20mountains%20because%20the%20mountains%20belonged%20to%20the%20Kirthar%20area.%20Yet%2C%20currently%2C%20trolley%20trucks%20and%20bulldozers%20are%20moving%20in%20the%20area%2C%20collecting%20sand%20and%20cutting%20down%20mountains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20locals%20have%20a%20lot%20to%20say%20about%20Bahria%20Town%2C%20expressing%20how%20everything%20that%20belongs%20to%20them%20is%20taken%20away.%20On%20the%20way%20to%20Mur%20Muradi%2C%20protesters%20blocked%20the%20road%20at%20Bandicha%20stop%20and%20complained%20that%20the%20village%20had%20suffered%20for%20days%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20electricity.%20They%20could%20not%20harvest%20or%20perform%20other%20work.%20One%20protester%2C%20in%20grief%20and%20anger%2C%20mentioned%20that%20speaking%20to%20the%20media%20about%20Bahria%20Town%20could%20lead%20to%20Rangers%20and%20the%20police%20picking%20them%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20locals%20have%20reportedly%20suffered%20unjustly%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20Bahria%20Town%2C%20with%20allegations%20of%20tactics%20used%20to%20force%20them%20off%20their%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Pakistan%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20debate%20about%20local%20land%20being%20allocated%20to%20real%20estate%20firms%20and%20key%20institutes%20in%20the%20name%20of%20development.%20The%20Sindh%20and%20Balochistan%20provinces%20have%20grave%20concerns%20because%20their%20land%20and%20natural%20resources%20are%20being%20taken%20or%20exploited.%20The%20locals%20are%20losing%20their%20rights%20of%20possession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Jamshoro%20district%2C%20where%20Bahria%20Town%20has%20expanded%20its%20construction%2C%20the%20caretaker%20government%20in%20Sindh%20has%20allocated%2052%2C713%20acres%20of%20land%20to%20the%20army%20under%20the%20Green%20Corporate%20Initiative%20Limited%20project.%20The%20land%20should%20be%20given%20to%20farmers%2C%20and%20it%20is%20argued%20that%20it%20should%20not%20be%20allocated%20to%20real%20estate%20developers%2C%20and%20the%20army%2C%20whose%20primary%20role%20is%20to%20protect%20the%20borders%2C%20not%20engage%20in%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHafeez%20complained%20that%20he%20and%20his%20members%2C%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20had%20been%20warning%20that%20the%20land%20of%20Sindh%20would%20be%20taken%20away%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20transformation%20of%20locals%20into%20the%20minority.%20However%2C%20his%20concerns%20went%20unnoticed.%20Now%2C%20Sindh%20is%20witnessing%20how%20local%20land%20is%20being%20allocated%20to%20powerful%20quarters%20and%20real%20estate%20tycoons%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fanti-people-construction-projects-are-killing-pakistans-malir-say-locals%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Anti-people%E2%80%99%20Construction%20Projects%20Are%20Killing%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Malir%2C%20Say%20Locals%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBahria%20Town%20acquires%20more%20land%20than%20what%20was%20originally%20offered%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20people%20could%20see%20the%20expansion%20of%20Bahria%20Town%20in%20Malir%2C%20they%20could%20hardly%20fathom%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20land%20it%20had%20acquired.%20After%20Hafeez%E2%80%99s%20petition%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20Pakistan%20ordered%20a%20survey%20to%20determine%20the%20extent%20of%20land%20under%20Bahria%20Town.%20A%20copy%20of%20the%20survey%20report%2C%20which%20was%20submitted%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20has%20been%20seen%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20on%20March%2021%2C%202019%2C%20Bahria%20Town%20claimed%20that%20it%20was%20to%20receive%2016%2C896%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20the%20district%20Malir%2C%20which%20falls%20under%20the%20province%20of%20Sindh.%20However%2C%20it%20stated%20that%20it%20only%20received%2011%2C747%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20shortfall%20of%205%2C149%20acres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20report%20revealed%20that%20%E2%80%9CBahria%20Town%20is%20in%20possession%20of%2019%2C931.63%20acres%20%E2%80%93%2017%2C709.45%20acres%20in%20district%20Malir%20and%202%2C222.18%20acres%20in%20district%20Jamshoro.%20The%20unauthorised%20possession%20of%20land%20in%20Bahria%20Town%E2%80%99s%20possession%20is%203%2C035.63%20acres.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sindh%20government%20appears%20to%20be%20unaware%20that%20Bahria%20Town%20was%20illegally%20occupying%20additional%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%