63955%2Fimage-1619.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22975%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17163955%2Fimage-1619.png%20975w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17163955%2Fimage-1619-300x225.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689566%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22731%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Wildlife%20Department%20a%20signboard%20placed%20in%20Mur%20Muradi.%20Photo%3A%20Hafeez%20Baloch%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Ali%2C%20a%20local%2C%20said%20that%20the%20signboard%20was%20placed%20in%20his%20area%20Mur%20Muradi%2C%20and%20it%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Kirthar%20area.%20They%20were%20warned%20not%20to%20harm%20animals%20and%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOmer%20Darwesh%2C%20a%20geographic%20information%20system%20expert%2C%20associated%20with%20the%20Sindh%20Indigenous%20Alliance%2C%20has%20developed%20maps%20to%20expose%20Bahria%20Town%20and%20its%20construction%20in%20Kirthar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDarwesh%20questioned%20those%20who%20denied%20Mur%20Muradi%20was%20not%20part%20of%20Kirthar.%20He%20asked%20why%20they%20did%20not%20install%20a%20signboard%20on%20the%20main%20road%20of%20Gadap%20town.%20What%20was%20the%20use%20of%20a%20signboard%20inside%20the%20jungle%3F%20They%20placed%20a%20signboard%20in%20the%20jungle%20to%20inform%20locals%20that%20this%20area%20belonged%20to%20Kirthar.%20Now%20when%20Bahria%20Town%20was%20caught%20constructing%20in%20Mur%20Muradi%2C%20the%20government%20removed%20the%20signboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20areas%20where%20Bahria%20Town%20is%20under%20construction%2C%20they%20are%20not%20considered%20part%20of%20Kirthar.%20Tareh%20Goth%20and%20Faiz%20Mohammad%20Goth%20were%20not%20surveyed%20because%20they%20were%20under%20Kirthar%2C%20but%20other%20villages%20were%20counted.%20Why%20are%20the%20wildlife%20department%20employees%20in%20Faiz%20Mohammad%20village%20if%20it%20is%20not%20part%20of%20Kirthar%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20the%20Pacheran%20Mountain%20and%20the%20river%20fall%20under%20Kirthar.%20Despite%20this%2C%20officials%20deny%20considering%20them%20part%20of%20Kirthar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20boys%20had%20attempted%20to%20climb%20the%20Pacheran%20Mountain.%20They%20were%20detained%20by%20the%20wildlife%20department%20for%20two%20days%20and%20fined%20for%20violating%20the%20Kirthar%20area.%20The%20wildlife%20department%E2%80%99s%20inconsistency%20is%20evident%2C%20as%20it%20seems%20they%20yield%20to%20the%20tycoon%E2%80%99s%20influence%2C%20allowing%20him%20to%20disregard%20laws%20without%20any%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20criticised%20the%20government%20and%20recounted%20his%20meeting%20with%20officials.%20The%20government%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20provide%20travel%20logs%20crucial%20for%20the%20survey%2C%20casting%20doubt%20on%20their%20survey%20accuracy.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20revenue%20department%20lacks%20boundary%20information%20for%20Kirthar.%20While%20the%20Malir%20revenue%20department%20has%20some%20records%2C%20the%20Jamshoro%20branch%20has%20none.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20approached%20Kirthar%20director%20Qazi%20Naeem%20regarding%20Bahria%20Town%E2%80%99s%20construction%20in%20Kirthar.%20He%20neither%20denied%20nor%20accepted%20but%20instead%20mentioned%20that%20the%20survey%20is%20ongoing%2C%20and%20he%20cannot%20provide%20any%20comments%20until%20it%20is%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fpeoples-history-pakistan%5C%22%3EA%20People%E2%80%99s%20History%20of%20Pakistan%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHistorical%20sites%20being%20ruined%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20region%20where%20locals%20are%20struggling%20to%20maintain%20their%20connection%20to%20the%20land%2C%20the%20history%20inscribed%20in%20the%20stones%20and%20old%20pathways%20be