nt-schools-rural-india-science-labs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclosely-guarded%20secret%20to%20success%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20he%20smiles%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20isn%E2%80%99t%20one.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20journey%20of%20relentless%20hard%20work%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20a%20middle-class%20home%2C%20Kalpit%20says%20education%20was%20given%20prime%20importance.%20His%20father%2C%20a%20nurse%2C%20was%20adamant%20that%20his%20sons%20should%20have%20access%20to%20resources%20and%20opportunities%20that%20he%20had%20missed%20out%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Kalpit%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20from%20a%20very%20simple%20background.%20But%20even%20then%2C%20he%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20people%20in%20his%20community%20to%20get%20educated.%20He%20had%20big%20dreams%20of%20becoming%20a%20doctor%2C%20but%20medical%20coaching%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy%20in%20those%20days.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20become%20a%20nurse%20instead.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Kalpit%20prides%20himself%20on%20having%20a%20BTech%20degree%20from%20IIT%20Bombay%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332810%2Fkota-suicides-iit-jee-neet-coaching-classes-entrance-exams-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esought-after%20institutes%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20he%20credits%20his%20father%20for%20always%20having%20his%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20education%20being%20put%20on%20a%20pedestal%20in%20the%20family%2C%20Kalpit%E2%80%99s%20tryst%20with%20competitive%20exams%20began%20at%20an%20early%20age.%20The%20first%20of%20these%20was%20in%20Class%207.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20did%20he%20do%20exceptionally%20well%20but%20got%20a%20scholarship%20too.%20Unbeknownst%20to%20him%2C%20it%20was%20these%20successes%20that%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20his%20%3Ca%20